7298 Date.parseFunctions = {count:0};
7299 Date.parseRegexes = [];
7300 Date.formatFunctions = {count:0};
7301 
7302 Date.prototype.dateFormat = function(format) {
7303     if (Date.formatFunctions[format] == null) {
7304         Date.createNewFormat(format);
7305     }
7306     var func = Date.formatFunctions[format];
7307     return this[func]();
7308 }
7309 
7310 Date.createNewFormat = function(format) {
7311     var funcName = "format" + Date.formatFunctions.count++;
7312     Date.formatFunctions[format] = funcName;
7313     var code = "Date.prototype." + funcName + " = function(){return ";
7314     var special = false;
7315     var ch = '';
7316     for (var i = 0; i < format.length; ++i) {
7317         ch = format.charAt(i);
7318         if (!special && ch == "\\") {
7319             special = true;
7320         }
7321         else if (special) {
7322             special = false;
7323             code += "'" + String.escape(ch) + "' + ";
7324         }
7325         else {
7326             code += Date.getFormatCode(ch);
7327         }
7328     }
7329     eval(code.substring(0, code.length - 3) + ";}");
7330 }
7331 
7332 Date.getFormatCode = function(character) {
7333     switch (character) {
7334     case "d":
7335         return "String.leftPad(this.getDate(), 2, '0') + ";
7336     case "D":
7337         return "Date.dayNames[this.getDay()].substring(0, 3) + ";
7338     case "j":
7339         return "this.getDate() + ";
7340     case "l":
7341         return "Date.dayNames[this.getDay()] + ";
7342     case "S":
7343         return "this.getSuffix() + ";
7344     case "w":
7345         return "this.getDay() + ";
7346     case "z":
7347         return "this.getDayOfYear() + ";
7348     case "W":
7349         return "this.getWeekOfYear() + ";
7350     case "F":
7351         return "Date.monthNames[this.getMonth()] + ";
7352     case "m":
7353         return "String.leftPad(this.getMonth() + 1, 2, '0') + ";
7354     case "M":
7355         return "Date.monthNames[this.getMonth()].substring(0, 3) + ";
7356     case "n":
7357         return "(this.getMonth() + 1) + ";
7358     case "t":
7359         return "this.getDaysInMonth() + ";
7360     case "L":
7361         return "(this.isLeapYear() ? 1 : 0) + ";
7362     case "Y":
7363         return "this.getFullYear() + ";
7364     case "y":
7365         return "('' + this.getFullYear()).substring(2, 4) + ";
7366     case "a":
7367         return "(this.getHours() < 12 ? 'am' : 'pm') + ";
7368     case "A":
7369         return "(this.getHours() < 12 ? 'AM' : 'PM') + ";
7370     case "g":
7371         return "((this.getHours() %12) ? this.getHours() % 12 : 12) + ";
7372     case "G":
7373         return "this.getHours() + ";
7374     case "h":
7375         return "String.leftPad((this.getHours() %12) ? this.getHours() % 12 : 12, 2, '0') + ";
7376     case "H":
7377         return "String.leftPad(this.getHours(), 2, '0') + ";
7378     case "i":
7379         return "String.leftPad(this.getMinutes(), 2, '0') + ";
7380     case "s":
7381         return "String.leftPad(this.getSeconds(), 2, '0') + ";
7382     case "O":
7383         return "this.getGMTOffset() + ";
7384     case "T":
7385         return "this.getTimezone() + ";
7386     case "Z":
7387         return "(this.getTimezoneOffset() * -60) + ";
7388     default:
7389         return "'" + String.escape(character) + "' + ";
7390     }
7391 }
7392 
7393 Date.parseDate = function(input, format) {
7394     if (Date.parseFunctions[format] == null) {
7395         Date.createParser(format);
7396     }
7397     var func = Date.parseFunctions[format];
7398     return Date[func](input);
7399 }
7400 
7401 Date.createParser = function(format) {
7402     var funcName = "parse" + Date.parseFunctions.count++;
7403     var regexNum = Date.parseRegexes.length;
7404     var currentGroup = 1;
7405     Date.parseFunctions[format] = funcName;
7406 
7407     var code = "Date." + funcName + " = function(input){\n"
7408         + "var y = -1, m = -1, d = -1, h = -1, i = -1, s = -1;\n"
7409         + "var d = new Date();\n"
7410         + "y = d.getFullYear();\n"
7411         + "m = d.getMonth();\n"
7412         + "d = d.getDate();\n"
7413         + "var results = input.match(Date.parseRegexes[" + regexNum + "]);\n"
7414         + "if (results && results.length > 0) {"
7415     var regex = "";
7416 
7417     var special = false;
7418     var ch = '';
7419     for (var i = 0; i < format.length; ++i) {
7420         ch = format.charAt(i);
7421         if (!special && ch == "\\") {
7422             special = true;
7423         }
7424         else if (special) {
7425             special = false;
7426             regex += String.escape(ch);
7427         }
7428         else {
7429             obj = Date.formatCodeToRegex(ch, currentGroup);
7430             currentGroup += obj.g;
7431             regex += obj.s;
7432             if (obj.g && obj.c) {
7433                 code += obj.c;
7434             }
7435         }
7436     }
7437 
7438     code += "if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0 && h >= 0 && i >= 0 && s >= 0)\n"
7439         + "{return new Date(y, m, d, h, i, s);}\n"
7440         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0 && h >= 0 && i >= 0)\n"
7441         + "{return new Date(y, m, d, h, i);}\n"
7442         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0 && h >= 0)\n"
7443         + "{return new Date(y, m, d, h);}\n"
7444         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0 && d > 0)\n"
7445         + "{return new Date(y, m, d);}\n"
7446         + "else if (y > 0 && m >= 0)\n"
7447         + "{return new Date(y, m);}\n"
7448         + "else if (y > 0)\n"
7449         + "{return new Date(y);}\n"
7450         + "}return null;}";
7451 
7452     Date.parseRegexes[regexNum] = new RegExp("^" + regex + "$");
7453     eval(code);
7454 }
7455 
7456 Date.formatCodeToRegex = function(character, currentGroup) {
7457     switch (character) {
7458     case "D":
7459         return {g:0,
7460         c:null,
7461         s:"(?:Sun|Mon|Tue|Wed|Thu|Fri|Sat)"};
7462     case "j":
7463     case "d":
7464         return {g:1,
7465             c:"d = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
7466             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
7467     case "l":
7468         return {g:0,
7469             c:null,
7470             s:"(?:" + Date.dayNames.join("|") + ")"};
7471     case "S":
7472         return {g:0,
7473             c:null,
7474             s:"(?:st|nd|rd|th)"};
7475     case "w":
7476         return {g:0,
7477             c:null,
7478             s:"\\d"};
7479     case "z":
7480         return {g:0,
7481             c:null,
7482             s:"(?:\\d{1,3})"};
7483     case "W":
7484         return {g:0,
7485             c:null,
7486             s:"(?:\\d{2})"};
7487     case "F":
7488         return {g:1,
7489             c:"m = parseInt(Date.monthNumbers[results[" + currentGroup + "].substring(0, 3)], 10);\n",
7490             s:"(" + Date.monthNames.join("|") + ")"};
7491     case "M":
7492         return {g:1,
7493             c:"m = parseInt(Date.monthNumbers[results[" + currentGroup + "]], 10);\n",
7494             s:"(Jan|Feb|Mar|Apr|May|Jun|Jul|Aug|Sep|Oct|Nov|Dec)"};
7495     case "n":
7496     case "m":
7497         return {g:1,
7498             c:"m = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10) - 1;\n",
7499             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
7500     case "t":
7501         return {g:0,
7502             c:null,
7503             s:"\\d{1,2}"};
7504     case "L":
7505         return {g:0,
7506             c:null,
7507             s:"(?:1|0)"};
7508     case "Y":
7509         return {g:1,
7510             c:"y = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
7511             s:"(\\d{4})"};
7512     case "y":
7513         return {g:1,
7514             c:"var ty = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n"
7515                 + "y = ty > Date.y2kYear ? 1900 + ty : 2000 + ty;\n",
7516             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
7517     case "a":
7518         return {g:1,
7519             c:"if (results[" + currentGroup + "] == 'am') {\n"
7520                 + "if (h == 12) { h = 0; }\n"
7521                 + "} else { if (h < 12) { h += 12; }}",
7522             s:"(am|pm)"};
7523     case "A":
7524         return {g:1,
7525             c:"if (results[" + currentGroup + "] == 'AM') {\n"
7526                 + "if (h == 12) { h = 0; }\n"
7527                 + "} else { if (h < 12) { h += 12; }}",
7528             s:"(AM|PM)"};
7529     case "g":
7530     case "G":
7531     case "h":
7532     case "H":
7533         return {g:1,
7534             c:"h = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
7535             s:"(\\d{1,2})"};
7536     case "i":
7537         return {g:1,
7538             c:"i = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
7539             s:"(\\d{2})"};
7540     case "s":
7541         return {g:1,
7542             c:"s = parseInt(results[" + currentGroup + "], 10);\n",
7543             s:"(\\d{2})"};
7544     case "O":
7545         return {g:0,
7546             c:null,
7547             s:"[+-]\\d{4}"};
7548     case "T":
7549         return {g:0,
7550             c:null,
7551             s:"[A-Z]{3}"};
7552     case "Z":
7553         return {g:0,
7554             c:null,
7555             s:"[+-]\\d{1,5}"};
7556     default:
7557         return {g:0,
7558             c:null,
7559             s:String.escape(character)};
7560     }
7561 }
7562 
7563 Date.prototype.getTimezone = function() {
7564     return this.toString().replace(
7565         /^.*? ([A-Z]{3}) [0-9]{4}.*$/, "$1").replace(
7566         /^.*?\(([A-Z])[a-z]+ ([A-Z])[a-z]+ ([A-Z])[a-z]+\)$/, "$1$2$3");
7567 }
7568 
7569 Date.prototype.getGMTOffset = function() {
7570     return (this.getTimezoneOffset() > 0 ? "-" : "+")
7571         + String.leftPad(Math.floor(this.getTimezoneOffset() / 60), 2, "0")
7572         + String.leftPad(this.getTimezoneOffset() % 60, 2, "0");
7573 }
7574 
7575 Date.prototype.getDayOfYear = function() {
7576     var num = 0;
7577     Date.daysInMonth[1] = this.isLeapYear() ? 29 : 28;
7578     for (var i = 0; i < this.getMonth(); ++i) {
7579         num += Date.daysInMonth[i];
7580     }
7581     return num + this.getDate() - 1;
7582 }
7583 
7584 Date.prototype.getWeekOfYear = function() {
7585     // Skip to Thursday of this week
7586     var now = this.getDayOfYear() + (5 - this.getDay());
7587     // Find the first Thursday of the year
7588     var jan1 = new Date(this.getFullYear(), 0, 1);
7589     var then = (5 - jan1.getDay());
7590     return String.leftPad(((now - then) / 7) + 1, 2, "0");
7591 }
7592 
7593 Date.prototype.isLeapYear = function() {
7594     var year = this.getFullYear();
7595     return ((year & 3) == 0 && (year % 100 || (year % 400 == 0 && year)));
7596 }
7597 
7598 Date.prototype.getFirstDayOfMonth = function() {
7599     var day = (this.getDay() - (this.getDate() - 1)) % 7;
7600     return (day < 0) ? (day + 7) : day;
7601 }
7602 
7603 Date.prototype.getLastDayOfMonth = function() {
7604     var day = (this.getDay() + (Date.daysInMonth[this.getMonth()] - this.getDate())) % 7;
7605     return (day < 0) ? (day + 7) : day;
7606 }
7607 
7608 Date.prototype.getDaysInMonth = function() {
7609     Date.daysInMonth[1] = this.isLeapYear() ? 29 : 28;
7610     return Date.daysInMonth[this.getMonth()];
7611 }
7612 
7613 Date.prototype.getSuffix = function() {
7614     switch (this.getDate()) {
7615         case 1:
7616         case 21:
7617         case 31:
7618             return "st";
7619         case 2:
7620         case 22:
7621             return "nd";
7622         case 3:
7623         case 23:
7624             return "rd";
7625         default:
7626             return "th";
7627     }
7628 }
7629 
7630 String.escape = function(string) {
7631     return string.replace(/('|\\)/g, "\\$1");
7632 }
7633 
7634 String.leftPad = function (val, size, ch) {
7635     var result = new String(val);
7636     if (ch == null) {
7637         ch = " ";
7638     }
7639     while (result.length < size) {
7640         result = ch + result;
7641     }
7642     return result;
7643 }

7693 /*
7694     json2.js
7695     2008-01-17
7696 
7697     Public Domain
7698 
7699     No warranty expressed or implied. Use at your own risk.
7700 
7701     See http://www.JSON.org/js.html
7702 
7703     This file creates a global JSON object containing two methods:
7704 
7705         JSON.stringify(value, whitelist)
7706             value       any JavaScript value, usually an object or array.
7707 
7708             whitelist   an optional array prameter that determines how object
7709                         values are stringified.
7710 
7711             This method produces a JSON text from a JavaScript value.
7712             There are three possible ways to stringify an object, depending
7713             on the optional whitelist parameter.
7714 
7715             If an object has a toJSON method, then the toJSON() method will be
7716             called. The value returned from the toJSON method will be
7717             stringified.
7718 
7719             Otherwise, if the optional whitelist parameter is an array, then
7720             the elements of the array will be used to select members of the
7721             object for stringification.
7722 
7723             Otherwise, if there is no whitelist parameter, then all of the
7724             members of the object will be stringified.
7725 
7726             Values that do not have JSON representaions, such as undefined or
7727             functions, will not be serialized. Such values in objects will be
7728             dropped; in arrays will be replaced with null.
7729             JSON.stringify(undefined) returns undefined. Dates will be
7730             stringified as quoted ISO dates.
7731 
7732             Example:
7733 
7734             var text = JSON.stringify(['e', {pluribus: 'unum'}]);
7735             // text is '["e",{"pluribus":"unum"}]'
7736 
7737         JSON.parse(text, filter)
7738             This method parses a JSON text to produce an object or
7739             array. It can throw a SyntaxError exception.
7740 
7741             The optional filter parameter is a function that can filter and
7742             transform the results. It receives each of the keys and values, and
7743             its return value is used instead of the original value. If it
7744             returns what it received, then structure is not modified. If it
7745             returns undefined then the member is deleted.
7746 
7747             Example:
7748 
7749             // Parse the text. If a key contains the string 'date' then
7750             // convert the value to a date.
7751 
7752             myData = JSON.parse(text, function (key, value) {
7753                 return key.indexOf('date') >= 0 ? new Date(value) : value;
7754             });
7755 
7756     This is a reference implementation. You are free to copy, modify, or
7757     redistribute.
7758 
7759     Use your own copy. It is extremely unwise to load third party
7760     code into your pages.
7761 */
7762 
7763 /*jslint evil: true */
7764 
7765 /*global JSON */
7766 
7767 /*members "\b", "\t", "\n", "\f", "\r", "\"", JSON, "\\", apply,
7768     charCodeAt, floor, getUTCDate, getUTCFullYear, getUTCHours,
7769     getUTCMinutes, getUTCMonth, getUTCSeconds, hasOwnProperty, join, length,
7770     parse, propertyIsEnumerable, prototype, push, replace, stringify, test,
7771     toJSON, toString
7772 */
7773 
7774 if (!this.JSON) {
7775 
7776     JSON = function () {
7777 
7778         function f(n) {    // Format integers to have at least two digits.
7779             return n < 10 ? '0' + n : n;
7780         }
7781 
7782         Date.prototype.toJSON = function () {
7783 
7784 // Eventually, this method will be based on the date.toISOString method.
7785 
7786             return this.getUTCFullYear()   + '-' +
7787                  f(this.getUTCMonth() + 1) + '-' +
7788                  f(this.getUTCDate())      + 'T' +
7789                  f(this.getUTCHours())     + ':' +
7790                  f(this.getUTCMinutes())   + ':' +
7791                  f(this.getUTCSeconds())   + 'Z';
7792         };
7793 
7794 
7795         var m = {    // table of character substitutions
7796             '\b': '\\b',
7797             '\t': '\\t',
7798             '\n': '\\n',
7799             '\f': '\\f',
7800             '\r': '\\r',
7801             '"' : '\\"',
7802             '\\': '\\\\'
7803         };
7804 
7805         function stringify(value, whitelist) {
7806             var a,          // The array holding the partial texts.
7807                 i,          // The loop counter.
7808                 k,          // The member key.
7809                 l,          // Length.
7810                 r = /["\\\x00-\x1f\x7f-\x9f]/g,
7811                 v;          // The member value.
7812 
7813             switch (typeof value) {
7814             case 'string':
7815 
7816 // If the string contains no control characters, no quote characters, and no
7817 // backslash characters, then we can safely slap some quotes around it.
7818 // Otherwise we must also replace the offending characters with safe sequences.
7819 
7820                 return r.test(value) ?
7821                     '"' + value.replace(r, function (a) {
7822                         var c = m[a];
7823                         if (c) {
7824                             return c;
7825                         }
7826                         c = a.charCodeAt();
7827                         return '\\u00' + Math.floor(c / 16).toString(16) +
7828                                                    (c % 16).toString(16);
7829                     }) + '"' :
7830                     '"' + value + '"';
7831 
7832             case 'number':
7833 
7834 // JSON numbers must be finite. Encode non-finite numbers as null.
7835 
7836                 return isFinite(value) ? String(value) : 'null';
7837 
7838             case 'boolean':
7839             case 'null':
7840                 return String(value);
7841 
7842             case 'object':
7843 
7844 // Due to a specification blunder in ECMAScript,
7845 // typeof null is 'object', so watch out for that case.
7846 
7847                 if (!value) {
7848                     return 'null';
7849                 }
7850 
7851 // If the object has a toJSON method, call it, and stringify the result.
7852 
7853                 if (typeof value.toJSON === 'function') {
7854                     return stringify(value.toJSON());
7855                 }
7856                 a = [];
7857                 if (typeof value.length === 'number' &&
7858                         !(value.propertyIsEnumerable('length'))) {
7859 
7860 // The object is an array. Stringify every element. Use null as a placeholder
7861 // for non-JSON values.
7862 
7863                     l = value.length;
7864                     for (i = 0; i < l; i += 1) {
7865                         a.push(stringify(value[i], whitelist) || 'null');
7866                     }
7867 
7868 // Join all of the elements together and wrap them in brackets.
7869 
7870                     return '[' + a.join(',') + ']';
7871                 }
7872                 if (whitelist) {
7873 
7874 // If a whitelist (array of keys) is provided, use it to select the components
7875 // of the object.
7876 
7877                     l = whitelist.length;
7878                     for (i = 0; i < l; i += 1) {
7879                         k = whitelist[i];
7880                         if (typeof k === 'string') {
7881                             v = stringify(value[k], whitelist);
7882                             if (v) {
7883                                 a.push(stringify(k) + ':' + v);
7884                             }
7885                         }
7886                     }
7887                 } else {
7888 
7889 // Otherwise, iterate through all of the keys in the object.
7890 
7891                     for (k in value) {
7892                         if (typeof k === 'string') {
7893                             v = stringify(value[k], whitelist);
7894                             if (v) {
7895                                 a.push(stringify(k) + ':' + v);
7896                             }
7897                         }
7898                     }
7899                 }
7900 
7901 // Join all of the member texts together and wrap them in braces.
7902 
7903                 return '{' + a.join(',') + '}';
7904             }
7905         }
7906 
7907         return {
7908             stringify: stringify,
7909             parse: function (text, filter) {
7910                 var j;
7911 
7912                 function walk(k, v) {
7913                     var i, n;
7914                     if (v && typeof v === 'object') {
7915                         for (i in v) {
7916                             if (Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.apply(v, [i])) {
7917                                 n = walk(i, v[i]);
7918                                 if (n !== undefined) {
7919                                     v[i] = n;
7920                                 }
7921                             }
7922                         }
7923                     }
7924                     return filter(k, v);
7925                 }
7926 
7927 
7928 // Parsing happens in three stages. In the first stage, we run the text against
7929 // regular expressions that look for non-JSON patterns. We are especially
7930 // concerned with '()' and 'new' because they can cause invocation, and '='
7931 // because it can cause mutation. But just to be safe, we want to reject all
7932 // unexpected forms.
7933 
7934 // We split the first stage into 4 regexp operations in order to work around
7935 // crippling inefficiencies in IE's and Safari's regexp engines. First we
7936 // replace all backslash pairs with '@' (a non-JSON character). Second, we
7937 // replace all simple value tokens with ']' characters. Third, we delete all
7938 // open brackets that follow a colon or comma or that begin the text. Finally,
7939 // we look to see that the remaining characters are only whitespace or ']' or
7940 // ',' or ':' or '{' or '}'. If that is so, then the text is safe for eval.
7941 
7942                 if (/^[\],:{}\s]*$/.test(text.replace(/\\./g, '@').
7943 replace(/"[^"\\\n\r]*"|true|false|null|-?\d+(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][+\-]?\d+)?/g, ']').
7944 replace(/(?:^|:|,)(?:\s*\[)+/g, ''))) {
7945 
7946 // In the second stage we use the eval function to compile the text into a
7947 // JavaScript structure. The '{' operator is subject to a syntactic ambiguity
7948 // in JavaScript: it can begin a block or an object literal. We wrap the text
7949 // in parens to eliminate the ambiguity.
7950 
7951                     j = eval('(' + text + ')');
7952 
7953 // In the optional third stage, we recursively walk the new structure, passing
7954 // each name/value pair to a filter function for possible transformation.
7955 
7956                     return typeof filter === 'function' ? walk('', j) : j;
7957                 }
7958 
7959 // If the text is not JSON parseable, then a SyntaxError is thrown.
7960 
7961                 throw new SyntaxError('parseJSON');
7962             }
7963         };
7964     }();
7965 }

7993 In2iGui.browser.msie7 = navigator.userAgent.indexOf('MSIE 7')!=-1;
7994 In2iGui.browser.webkit = navigator.userAgent.indexOf('WebKit')!=-1;
7995 In2iGui.browser.gecko = !In2iGui.browser.webkit && navigator.userAgent.indexOf('Gecko')!=-1;
7996 
7997 /**
7998  * Gets the one instance of In2iGui
7999  */
8000 In2iGui.get = function(name) {
8001 	if (!In2iGui.instance) {
8002 		In2iGui.instance = new In2iGui();
8003 	}
8004 	if (name) {
8005 		return In2iGui.instance.objects.get(name);
8006 	} else {
8007 		return In2iGui.instance;
8008 	}
8009 }

8011 document.observe('dom:loaded', function() {In2iGui.get().ignite();});

8013 In2iGui.dwrErrorhandler = function(msg,e) {
8014 	n2i.log(msg);
8015 	n2i.log(e);
8016 	In2iGui.get().showAlert({title:'An unexpected error occurred!',text:msg,emotion:'gasp'});
8017 }

8019 In2iGui.prototype = {
8020 	ignite : function(id) {
8021 		if (window.dwr) {
8022 			if (dwr && dwr.engine && dwr.engine.setErrorHandler) {
8023 				dwr.engine.setErrorHandler(In2iGui.dwrErrorhandler);
8024 			}
8025 		}
8026 		this.domLoaded = true;
8027 		In2iGui.domReady = true;
8028 		this.resize();
8029 		In2iGui.callSuperDelegates(this,'interfaceIsReady');
8030 	},
8031 	addBehavior : function(id) {
8032 		var self = this;
8033 		Event.observe(window,'resize',function() {
8034 			self.resize();
8035 		});
8036 	},
8037 	addDelegate : function(delegate) {
8038 		this.delegates[this.delegates.length] = delegate;
8039 	},
8040 	getTopPad : function(element) {
8041 		var pad = 0;
8042 		var all = parseInt(n2i.getStyle(element,'padding'));
8043 		var top = parseInt(n2i.getStyle(element,'padding-top'));
8044 		if (all) pad+=all;
8045 		if (top) pad+=top;
8046 		return pad;
8047 	},
8048 	getBottomPad : function(element) {
8049 		var pad = 0;
8050 		var all = parseInt(n2i.getStyle(element,'padding'));
8051 		var bottom = parseInt(n2i.getStyle(element,'padding-bottom'));
8052 		if (all) pad+=all;
8053 		if (bottom) pad+=bottom;
8054 		return pad;
8055 	},
8056 	resize : function(id) {
8057 		if (!this.overflows) return;
8058 		var height = n2i.getInnerHeight();
8059 		this.overflows.each(function(overflow) {
8060 			if (n2i.browser.webkit || n2i.browser.gecko) {
8061 				overflow.element.style.display='none';
8062 				overflow.element.style.width = overflow.element.parentNode.clientWidth+'px';
8063 				overflow.element.style.display='';
8064 			}
8065 			overflow.element.style.height = height+overflow.diff+'px';
8066 		});
8067 	},
8068 	registerOverflow : function(id,diff) {
8069 		if (!this.overflows) this.overflows=[];
8070 		var overflow = $(id);
8071 		this.overflows.push({element:overflow,diff:diff});
8072 	},
8073 	alert : function(options,callBack) {
8074 		if (!this.alertBox) {
8075 			this.alertBox = In2iGui.Alert.create(null,options);
8076 			this.alertBoxButton = In2iGui.Button.create('in2iGuiAlertBoxButton',{text : 'OK'});
8077 			this.alertBoxButton.addDelegate(this);
8078 			this.alertBox.addButton(this.alertBoxButton);
8079 		} else {
8080 			this.alertBox.update(options);
8081 		}
8082 		this.alertBoxCallBack = callBack;
8083 		this.alertBoxButton.setText(options.button ? options.button : 'OK')
8084 		this.alertBox.show();
8085 	},
8086 	click$in2iGuiAlertBoxButton : function() {
8087 		In2iGui.get().alertBox.hide();
8088 		if (this.alertBoxCallBack) {
8089 			this.alertBoxCallBack();
8090 			this.alertBoxCallBack = null;
8091 		}
8092 	},
8093 	/** @deprecated */
8094 	showAlert : function(options) {
8095 		this.alert(options);
8096 	},
8097 	confirm : function(name,options) {
8098 		var alert = In2iGui.get(name);
8099 		if (!alert) {
8100 			alert = In2iGui.Alert.create(name,options);
8101 			var cancel = In2iGui.Button.create(name+'_cancel',{text : options.cancel || 'Cancel',highlighted:options.highlighted=='cancel'});
8102 			cancel.addDelegate({buttonWasClicked:function(){
8103 				In2iGui.get(name).hide();
8104 				In2iGui.callDelegates(In2iGui.get(name),'cancel');
8105 			}});
8106 			alert.addButton(cancel);
8107 		
8108 			var ok = In2iGui.Button.create(name+'_ok',{text : options.ok || 'OK',highlighted:options.highlighted=='ok'});
8109 			ok.addDelegate({buttonWasClicked:function(){
8110 				In2iGui.get(name).hide();
8111 				In2iGui.callDelegates(In2iGui.get(name),'ok');
8112 			}});
8113 			alert.addButton(ok);
8114 		} else {
8115 			alert.update(options);
8116 			In2iGui.get(name+'_ok').setText(options.ok || 'ok');
8117 			In2iGui.get(name+'_ok').setHighlighted(options.highlighted=='ok');
8118 			In2iGui.get(name+'_cancel').setText(options.ok || 'cancel');
8119 			In2iGui.get(name+'_cancel').setHighlighted(options.highlighted=='cancel');
8120 			if (options.cancel) In2iGui.get(name+'_cancel').setText(options.cancel);
8121 		}
8122 		alert.show();
8123 	},
8124 	changeState : function(state) {
8125 		if (this.state==state) return;
8126 		var objects = this.objects.values();
8127 		objects.each(function(obj) {
8128 			if (obj.state) {
8129 				if (obj.state==state) obj.show();
8130 				else obj.hide();
8131 			}
8132 		});
8133 	},
8134 	getDescendants : function(widget) {
8135 		var desc = [];
8136 		var e = widget.getElement();
8137 		if (e) {
8138 			var d = e.descendants();
8139 			var self = this;
8140 			d.each(function(node) {
8141 				self.objects.values().each(function(obj) {
8142 					if (obj.getElement()==node) {
8143 						desc.push(obj);
8144 					}
8145 				})
8146 			});
8147 		}
8148 		return desc;
8149 	},
8150 	getAncestors : function(widget) {
8151 		var desc = [];
8152 		var e = widget.getElement();
8153 		if (e) {
8154 			var d = e.ancestors();
8155 			d.each(function(node) {
8156 				this.objects.values().each(function(obj) {
8157 					if (obj.getElement()==node) {
8158 						desc.push(obj);
8159 					}
8160 				})
8161 			}.bind(this));
8162 		}
8163 		return desc;
8164 	}
8165 }

8195 			}

8214 in2igui.showMessage = function(msg) {
8215 	if (!In2iGui.message) {
8216 		In2iGui.message = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_message'}).update('<div><div></div></div>');
8217 		document.body.appendChild(In2iGui.message);
8218 	}
8219 	In2iGui.message.select('div')[1].update(msg);
8220 	In2iGui.message.setStyle({'display':'block',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex()});
8221 	if (!In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8222 		In2iGui.message.setStyle({opacity:0});
8223 	}
8224 	In2iGui.message.setStyle({marginLeft:(In2iGui.message.getWidth()/-2)+'px',marginTop:n2i.getScrollTop()+'px'});
8225 	if (!In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8226 		n2i.ani(In2iGui.message,'opacity',1,300);
8227 	}
8228 }

8232 		if (!In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8233 			n2i.ani(In2iGui.message,'opacity',0,300,{hideOnComplete:true});
8234 		} else {
8235 			In2iGui.message.setStyle({display:'none'});
8236 		}
8237 	}

8240 in2igui.showToolTip = function(options) {
8241 	var key = options.key || 'common';
8242 	var t = In2iGui.toolTips[key];
8243 	if (!t) {
8244 		t = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_tooltip'}).update('<div><div></div></div>').setStyle({display:'none'});
8245 		document.body.appendChild(t);
8246 		In2iGui.toolTips[key] = t;
8247 	}
8248 	t.onclick = function() {in2igui.hideToolTip(options)};
8249 	var n = $(options.element);
8250 	var pos = n.cumulativeOffset();
8251 	t.select('div')[1].update(options.text);
8252 	if (t.style.display=='none' && !In2iGui.browser.msie) t.setStyle({opacity:0});
8253 	t.setStyle({'display':'block',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex()});
8254 	t.setStyle({left:(pos.left-t.getWidth()+4)+'px',top:(pos.top+2-(t.getHeight()/2)+(n.getHeight()/2))+'px'});
8255 	if (!In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8256 		n2i.ani(t,'opacity',1,300);
8257 	}
8258 }
8259 
8260 in2igui.hideToolTip = function(options) {
8261 	var key = options ? options.key || 'common' : 'common';
8262 	var t = In2iGui.toolTips[key];
8263 	if (t) {
8264 		if (!In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8265 			n2i.ani(t,'opacity',0,300,{hideOnComplete:true});
8266 		} else {
8267 			t.setStyle({display:'none'});
8268 		}
8269 	}
8270 }

8274 In2iGui.isWithin = function(e,element) {
8275 	Event.extend(e);
8276 	var offset = element.cumulativeOffset();
8277 	var dims = element.getDimensions();
8278 	return e.pointerX()>offset.left && e.pointerX()<offset.left+dims.width && e.pointerY()>offset.top && e.pointerY()<offset.top+dims.height;
8279 }

8294 		return;

8331 //////////////////////////// Positioning /////////////////////////////

8333 In2iGui.positionAtElement = function(element,target,options) {
8334 	options = options || {};
8335 	element = $(element);
8336 	target = $(target);
8337 	var origDisplay = element.getStyle('display');
8338 	if (origDisplay=='none') {
8339 		element.setStyle({'visibility':'hidden','display':'block'});
8340 	}
8341 	var pos = target.cumulativeOffset(),left = pos.left,top = pos.top;
8342 	var vert=options.vertical || null;
8343 	if (options.horizontal && options.horizontal=='right') {
8344 		left = left+target.getWidth()-element.getWidth();
8345 	}
8346 	if (vert=='topOutside') {
8347 		top = top-element.getHeight();
8348 	} else if (vert=='bottomOutside') {
8349 		top = top+target.getHeight();
8350 	}
8351 	left+=(options.left || 0);
8352 	top+=(options.top || 0);
8353 	element.setStyle({'left':left+'px','top':top+'px'});
8354 	if (origDisplay=='none') {
8355 		element.setStyle({'visibility':'visible','display':'none'});
8356 	}
8357 }

8362 In2iGui.getDragProxy = function() {
8363 	if (!In2iGui.dragProxy) {
8364 		In2iGui.dragProxy = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_dragproxy'}).setStyle({'display':'none'});
8365 		document.body.appendChild(In2iGui.dragProxy);
8366 	}
8367 	return In2iGui.dragProxy;
8368 }
8369 
8370 In2iGui.startDrag = function(e,element,options) {
8371 	var info = element.dragDropInfo;
8372 	In2iGui.dropTypes = In2iGui.findDropTypes(info);
8373 	if (!In2iGui.dropTypes) return;
8374 	var event = Event.extend(e);
8375 	var proxy = In2iGui.getDragProxy();
8376 	Event.observe(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.dragListener);
8377 	Event.observe(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.dragEndListener);
8378 	In2iGui.dragInfo = info;
8379 	if (info.icon) {
8380 		proxy.style.backgroundImage = 'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(info.icon,1)+')';
8381 	}
8382 	In2iGui.startDragPos = {top:event.pointerY(),left:event.pointerX()};
8383 	proxy.innerHTML = '<span>'+info.title+'</span>' || '###';
8384 	In2iGui.dragging = true;
8385 }
8386 
8387 In2iGui.findDropTypes = function(drag) {
8388 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
8389 	var drops = null;
8390 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
8391 		if (gui.delegates[i].dragDrop) {
8392 			for (var j=0; j < gui.delegates[i].dragDrop.length; j++) {
8393 				var rule = gui.delegates[i].dragDrop[j];
8394 				if (rule.drag==drag.kind) {
8395 					if (drops==null) drops={};
8396 					drops[rule.drop] = {};
8397 				}
8398 			};
8399 		}
8400 	}
8401 	return drops;
8402 }
8403 
8404 In2iGui.dragListener = function(e) {
8405 	var event = Event.extend(e);
8406 	In2iGui.dragProxy.style.left = (event.pointerX()+10)+'px';
8407 	In2iGui.dragProxy.style.top = event.pointerY()+'px';
8408 	In2iGui.dragProxy.style.display='block';
8409 	var target = In2iGui.findDropTarget(event.element());
8410 	if (target && In2iGui.dropTypes[target.dragDropInfo['kind']]) {
8411 		if (In2iGui.latestDropTarget) {
8412 			In2iGui.latestDropTarget.removeClassName('in2igui_drop');
8413 		}
8414 		target.addClassName('in2igui_drop');
8415 		In2iGui.latestDropTarget = target;
8416 	} else if (In2iGui.latestDropTarget) {
8417 		In2iGui.latestDropTarget.removeClassName('in2igui_drop');
8418 		In2iGui.latestDropTarget = null;
8419 	}
8420 	return false;
8421 }
8422 
8423 In2iGui.findDropTarget = function(node) {
8424 	while (node) {
8425 		if (node.dragDropInfo) {
8426 			return node;
8427 		}
8428 		node = node.parentNode;
8429 	}
8430 	return null;
8431 }
8432 
8433 In2iGui.dragEndListener = function(event) {
8434 	Event.stopObserving(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.dragListener);
8435 	Event.stopObserving(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.dragEndListener);
8436 	In2iGui.dragging = false;
8437 	if (In2iGui.latestDropTarget) {
8438 		In2iGui.latestDropTarget.removeClassName('in2igui_drop');
8439 		In2iGui.callDelegatesDrop(In2iGui.dragInfo,In2iGui.latestDropTarget.dragDropInfo);
8440 		In2iGui.dragProxy.style.display='none';
8441 	} else {
8442 		n2i.ani(In2iGui.dragProxy,'left',(In2iGui.startDragPos.left+10)+'px',200,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
8443 		n2i.ani(In2iGui.dragProxy,'top',(In2iGui.startDragPos.top-5)+'px',200,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow,hideOnComplete:true});
8444 	}
8445 	In2iGui.latestDropTarget=null;
8446 }
8447 
8448 In2iGui.dropOverListener = function(event) {
8449 	if (In2iGui.dragging) {
8450 		//this.style.backgroundColor='#3875D7';
8451 	}
8452 }
8453 
8454 In2iGui.dropOutListener = function(event) {
8455 	if (In2iGui.dragging) {
8456 		//this.style.backgroundColor='';
8457 	}
8458 }

8460 /* ****************** Delegating *************** */
8461 
8462 In2iGui.extend = function(obj) {
8463 	if (!obj.name) {
8464 		In2iGui.latestObjectIndex++;
8465 		obj.name = 'unnamed'+In2iGui.latestObjectIndex;
8466 	}
8467 	In2iGui.get().objects.set(obj.name,obj);
8468 	obj.delegates = [];
8469 	obj.addDelegate = function(delegate) {
8470 		n2i.addToArray(this.delegates,delegate);
8471 	}
8472 	obj.removeDelegate = function(delegate) {
8473 		n2i.removeFromArray(this.delegates,delegate);
8474 	}
8475 	obj.fire = function(method,value,event) {
8476 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,method,value,event);
8477 	}
8478 	if (!obj.getElement) {
8479 		obj.getElement = function() {
8480 			return this.element;
8481 		}
8482 	}
8483 	if (!obj.valueForProperty) {
8484 		obj.valueForProperty = function(p) {return this[p]};
8485 	}
8486 }
8487 
8488 In2iGui.callDelegatesDrop = function(dragged,dropped) {
8489 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
8490 	var result = null;
8491 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
8492 		if (gui.delegates[i]['drop$'+dragged.kind+'$'+dropped.kind]) {
8493 			gui.delegates[i]['drop$'+dragged.kind+'$'+dropped.kind](dragged,dropped);
8494 		}
8495 	}
8496 }
8497 
8498 In2iGui.callAncestors = function(obj,method,value,event) {
8499 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
8500 	var d = In2iGui.get().getAncestors(obj);
8501 	d.each(function(child) {
8502 		if (child[method]) {
8503 			thisResult = child[method](value,event);
8504 		}
8505 	});
8506 }
8507 
8508 In2iGui.callDescendants = function(obj,method,value,event) {
8509 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
8510 	var d = In2iGui.get().getDescendants(obj);
8511 	d.each(function(child) {
8512 		if (child[method]) {
8513 			thisResult = child[method](value,event);
8514 		}
8515 	});
8516 }
8517 
8518 In2iGui.callDelegates = function(obj,method,value,event) {
8519 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
8520 	var result = null;
8521 	if (obj.delegates) {
8522 		for (var i=0; i < obj.delegates.length; i++) {
8523 			var delegate = obj.delegates[i];
8524 			var thisResult = null;
8525 			if (obj.name && delegate[method+'$'+obj.name]) {
8526 				thisResult = delegate[method+'$'+obj.name](value,event);
8527 			} else if (obj.kind && delegate[method+'$'+obj.kind]) {
8528 				thisResult = delegate[method+'$'+obj.kind](value,event);
8529 			} else if (delegate[method]) {
8530 				thisResult = delegate[method](value,event);
8531 			}
8532 			if (result==null && thisResult!=null && typeof(thisResult)!='undefined') {
8533 				result = thisResult;
8534 			}
8535 		};
8536 	}
8537 	var superResult = In2iGui.callSuperDelegates(obj,method,value,event);
8538 	if (result==null && superResult!=null) result = superResult;
8539 	return result;
8540 }
8541 
8542 In2iGui.callSuperDelegates = function(obj,method,value,event) {
8543 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
8544 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
8545 	var result = null;
8546 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
8547 		var delegate = gui.delegates[i];
8548 		var thisResult = null;
8549 		if (obj.name && delegate[method+'$'+obj.name]) {
8550 			thisResult = delegate[method+'$'+obj.name](value,event);
8551 		} else if (obj.kind && delegate[method+'$'+obj.kind]) {
8552 			thisResult = delegate[method+'$'+obj.kind](value,event);
8553 		} else if (delegate[method]) {
8554 			thisResult = delegate[method](value,event);
8555 		}
8556 		if (result==null && thisResult!=null && typeof(thisResult)!='undefined') {
8557 			result = thisResult;
8558 		}
8559 	};
8560 	return result;
8561 }
8562 
8563 ////////////////////////////// Bindings ///////////////////////////
8564 
8565 In2iGui.firePropertyChange = function(obj,name,value) {
8566 	In2iGui.callDelegates(obj,'propertyChanged',{property:name,value:value});
8567 }
8568 
8569 In2iGui.bind = function(expression,delegate) {
8570 	if (expression.charAt(0)=='@') {
8571 		var pair = expression.substring(1).split('.');
8572 		var obj = eval(pair[0]);
8573 		var p = pair.slice(1).join('.');
8574 		obj.addDelegate({
8575 			propertyChanged : function(prop) {
8576 				if (prop.property==p) {
8577 					delegate(prop.value);
8578 				}
8579 			}
8580 		});
8581 		return obj.valueForProperty(p);
8582 	}
8583 	return expression;
8584 }
8585 
8586 //////////////////////////////// Data /////////////////////////////
8587 
8588 In2iGui.dwrUpdate = function() {
8589 	var func = arguments[0];
8590 	var delegate = {
8591   		callback:function(data) { In2iGui.handleDwrUpdate(data) }
8592 	}
8593 	var num = arguments.length;
8594 	if (num==1) {
8595 		func(delegate);
8596 	} else if (num==2) {
8597 		func(arguments[1],delegate);
8598 	} else {
8599 		alert('Too many parameters');
8600 	}
8601 }
8602 
8603 In2iGui.handleDwrUpdate = function(data) {
8604 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
8605 	for (var i=0; i < data.length; i++) {
8606 		if (gui.objects.get(data[i].name)) {
8607 			gui.objects.get(data[i].name).updateFromObject(data[i]);
8608 		}
8609 	};
8610 }
8611 
8612 In2iGui.update = function(url,delegate) {
8613 	var dlgt = {
8614 		onSuccess:function(t) {In2iGui.handleUpdate(t,delegate)}
8615 	}
8616 	$get(url,dlgt);
8617 }
8618 
8619 In2iGui.handleUpdate = function(t,delegate) {
8620 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
8621 	var doc = t.responseXML.firstChild;
8622 	var children = doc.childNodes;
8623 	for (var i=0; i < children.length; i++) {
8624 		if (children[i].nodeType==1) {
8625 			var name = children[i].getAttribute('name');
8626 			if (name && name!='' && gui.objects.get(name)) {
8627 				gui.objects.get(name).updateFromNode(children[i]);
8628 			}
8629 		}
8630 	};
8631 	delegate.onSuccess();
8632 }
8633 
8634 In2iGui.jsonResponse = function(t,key) {
8635 	if (!t.responseXML || !t.responseXML.documentElement) {
8636 		var str = t.responseText.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, '');
8637 		if (str.length>0) {
8638 			var json = t.responseText.evalJSON(true);
8639 		} else {
8640 			json = '';
8641 		}
8642 		In2iGui.callDelegates(json,'success$'+key)
8643 	} else {
8644 		In2iGui.callDelegates(t,'success$'+key)
8645 	}
8646 }
8647 
8648 In2iGui.json = function(data,url,delegateOrKey) {
8649 	var options = {method:'post',parameters:{}};
8650 	if (typeof(delegateOrKey)=='string') {
8651 		options.onSuccess=function(t) {In2iGui.jsonResponse(t,delegateOrKey)};
8652 	} else {
8653 		delegate = delegateOrKey;
8654 	}
8655 	for (key in data) {
8656 		options.parameters[key]=Object.toJSON(data[key])
8657 	}
8658 	new Ajax.Request(url,options)
8659 }
8660 
8661 In2iGui.parseItems = function(doc) {
8662 	var out = [];
8663 	var items = doc.getElementsByTagName('item');
8664 	for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
8665 		var item = items[i];
8666 		var title = item.getAttribute('title');
8667 		var value = item.getAttribute('value');
8668 		var icon = item.getAttribute('icon');
8669 		var kind = item.getAttribute('kind');
8670 		out.push({title:title,value:value,icon:icon,kind:kind});
8671 	}
8672 	return out;
8673 }

8675 ////////////////////////////////// Source ///////////////////////////
8676 
8677 In2iGui.Source = function(o) {
8678 	this.options = n2i.override({url:null,dwr:null},o);
8679 	this.name = o.name;
8680 	this.data = null;
8681 	this.parameters = [];
8682 	In2iGui.extend(this);
8683 	if (o.delegate) this.addDelegate(o.delegate);
8684 	this.busy=false;
8685 	n2i.log('new: '+o.url);
8686 	In2iGui.onDomReady(this.init.bind(this));
8687 }
8688 
8689 In2iGui.Source.prototype = {
8690 	init : function() {
8691 		n2i.log('init:'+this.delegates.length)
8692 		var self = this;
8693 		this.parameters.each(function(parm) {
8694 			parm.value = In2iGui.bind(parm.value,function(value) {
8695 				self.changeParameter(parm.key,value);
8696 			});
8697 		})
8698 		this.refresh();
8699 	},
8700 	refresh : function() {
8701 		if (this.delegates.length==0) return;
8702 		if (this.busy) {
8703 			this.pendingRefresh = true;
8704 			return;
8705 		}
8706 		this.pendingRefresh = false;
8707 		var self = this;
8708 		if (this.options.url) {
8709 			var url = new n2i.URL(this.options.url);
8710 			this.parameters.each(function(p) {
8711 				url.addParameter(p.key,p.value);
8712 			});
8713 			this.busy=true;
8714 			In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsBusy');
8715 			new Ajax.Request(url.toString(), {onSuccess: function(t) {self.parse(t)},onException:function(t,e) {n2i.log(e)}});
8716 		} else if (this.options.dwr) {
8717 			var pair = this.options.dwr.split('.');
8718 			var facade = eval(pair[0]);
8719 			var method = pair[1];
8720 			var args = facade[method].argumentNames();
8721 			for (var i=0; i < args.length; i++) {
8722 				if (this.parameters[i])
8723 					args[i]=this.parameters[i].value || null;
8724 			};
8725 			args[args.length-1]=function(r) {self.parseDWR(r)};
8726 			this.busy=true;
8727 			In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsBusy');
8728 			facade[method].apply(facade,args);
8729 		}
8730 	},
8731 	end : function() {
8732 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsNotBusy');
8733 		this.busy=false;
8734 		if (this.pendingRefresh) {
8735 			this.refresh();
8736 		}
8737 	},
8738 	parse : function(t) {
8739 		if (t.responseXML) {
8740 			this.parseXML(t.responseXML);
8741 		}
8742 		this.end();
8743 	},
8744 	parseXML : function(doc) {
8745 		if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='items') {
8746 			this.data = In2iGui.parseItems(doc);
8747 			this.fire('itemsLoaded',this.data);
8748 		} else if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='list') {
8749 			this.fire('listLoaded',doc);
8750 		}
8751 	},
8752 	parseDWR : function(data) {
8753 		this.data = data;
8754 		this.fire('objectsLoaded',data);
8755 		this.end();
8756 	},
8757 	addParameter : function(parm) {
8758 		this.parameters.push(parm);
8759 	},
8760 	changeParameter : function(key,value) {
8761 		this.parameters.each(function(p) {
8762 			if (p.key==key) p.value=value;
8763 		})
8764 		var self = this;
8765 		window.clearTimeout(this.paramDelay);
8766 		this.paramDelay = window.setTimeout(function() {
8767 			this.refresh();
8768 		}.bind(this),100)
8769 	}
8770 }

8780 In2iGui.TextField = function(id,name,options) {
8781 	this.options = n2i.override({placeholder:null,placeholderElement:null},options);
8782 	var e = this.element = $(id);
8783 	this.element.setAttribute('autocomplete','off');
8784 	this.value = this.element.value;
8785 	this.isPassword = this.element.type=='password';
8786 	this.name = name;
8787 	In2iGui.extend(this);
8788 	this.addBehavior();
8789 	if (this.options.placeholderElement && this.value!='') {
8790 		in2igui.fadeOut(this.options.placeholderElement,0);
8791 	}
8792 	this.checkPlaceholder();
8793 	if (e==document.activeElement) this.focused();
8794 }
8795 
8796 In2iGui.TextField.prototype = {
8797 	addBehavior : function() {
8798 		var self = this;
8799 		var e = this.element;
8800 		var p = this.options.placeholderElement;
8801 		e.observe('keyup',this.keyDidStrike.bind(this));
8802 		e.observe('focus',this.focused.bind(this));
8803 		e.observe('blur',this.checkPlaceholder.bind(this));
8804 		if (p) {
8805 			p.setStyle({cursor:'text'});
8806 			p.observe('mousedown',this.focus.bind(this)).observe('click',this.focus.bind(this));
8807 		}
8808 	},
8809 	focused : function() {
8810 		var e = this.element;
8811 		var p = this.options.placeholderElement;
8812 		if (p && e.value=='') {
8813 			in2igui.fadeOut(p,0);
8814 		}
8815 		if (e.value==this.options.placeholder) {
8816 			e.value='';
8817 			e.removeClassName('in2igui_placeholder');
8818 			if (this.isPassword && !In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8819 				e.type='password';
8820 				if (In2iGui.browser.webkit) {
8821 					e.select();
8822 				}
8823 			}
8824 		}
8825 		e.select();		
8826 	},
8827 	checkPlaceholder : function() {
8828 		if (this.options.placeholderElement && this.value=='') {
8829 			in2igui.fadeIn(this.options.placeholderElement,200);
8830 		}
8831 		if (this.options.placeholder && this.value=='') {
8832 			if (!this.isPassword || !In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8833 				this.element.value=this.options.placeholder;
8834 				this.element.addClassName('in2igui_placeholder');
8835 			}
8836 			if (this.isPassword && !In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8837 				this.element.type='text';
8838 			}
8839 		} else {
8840 			this.element.removeClassName('in2igui_placeholder');
8841 			if (this.isPassword && !In2iGui.browser.msie) {
8842 				this.element.type='password';
8843 			}
8844 		}
8845 	},
8846 	keyDidStrike : function() {
8847 		if (this.value!=this.element.value && this.element.value!=this.options.placeholder) {
8848 			this.value = this.element.value;
8849 			this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
8850 		}
8851 	},
8852 	getValue : function() {
8853 		return this.value;
8854 	},
8855 	setValue : function(value) {
8856 		if (value==undefined || value==null) value='';
8857 		this.value = value;
8858 		this.element.value = value;
8859 	},
8860 	isEmpty : function() {
8861 		return this.value=='';
8862 	},
8863 	isBlank : function() {
8864 		return this.value.strip()=='';
8865 	},
8866 	focus : function() {
8867 		this.element.focus();
8868 	},
8869 	setError : function(error) {
8870 		var isError = error ? true : false;
8871 		this.element.setClassName('in2igui_field_error',isError);
8872 		if (typeof(error) == 'string') {
8873 			in2igui.showToolTip({text:error,element:this.element,key:this.name});
8874 		}
8875 		if (!isError) {
8876 			in2igui.hideToolTip({key:this.name});
8877 		}
8878 	}
8879 }

8892 In2iGui.InfoView.create = function(name,options) {
8893 	options = options || {};
8894 	var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_infoview'});
8895 	if (options.height) {
8896 		element.setStyle({height:options.height+'px','overflow':'auto','overflowX':'hidden'});
8897 	}

8899 		element.setStyle({margin:options.margin+'px'});

8904 
8905 In2iGui.InfoView.prototype = {
8906 	addHeader : function(text) {
8907 		var row = new Element('tr');
8908 		row.insert(new Element('th',{'class' : 'in2igui_infoview_header','colspan':'2'}).insert(text));
8909 		this.body.insert(row);
8910 	},
8911 	addProperty : function(label,text) {
8912 		var row = new Element('tr');
8913 		row.insert(new Element('th').insert(label));
8914 		row.insert(new Element('td').insert(text));
8915 		this.body.insert(row);
8916 	},
8917 	addObjects : function(label,objects) {
8918 		if (!objects || objects.length==0) return;
8919 		var row = new Element('tr');
8920 		row.insert(new Element('th').insert(label));
8921 		var cell = new Element('td');
8922 		var click = this.options.clickObjects;
8923 		objects.each(function(obj) {
8924 			var node = new Element('div').insert(obj.title);
8925 			if (click) {
8926 				node.addClassName('in2igui_infoview_click')
8927 				node.observe('click',function() {
8928 					In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'objectWasClicked',obj);
8929 				});
8930 			}
8931 			cell.insert(node);
8932 		});
8933 		row.insert(cell);
8934 		this.body.insert(row);
8935 	},
8936 	setBusy : function(busy) {
8937 		if (busy) {
8938 			this.element.addClassName('in2igui_infoview_busy');
8939 		} else {
8940 			this.element.removeClassName('in2igui_infoview_busy');
8941 		}
8942 	},
8943 	clear : function() {
8944 		this.body.update();
8945 	},
8946 	update : function(data) {
8947 		this.clear();
8948 		for (var i=0; i < data.length; i++) {
8949 			switch (data[i].type) {
8950 				case 'header': this.addHeader(data[i].value); break;
8951 				case 'property': this.addProperty(data[i].label,data[i].value); break;
8952 				case 'objects': this.addObjects(data[i].label,data[i].value); break;
8953 			}
8954 		};
8955 	}
8956 }

8996 		'</div>');
8997 	document.body.appendChild(element);
8998 	return new In2iGui.Window(element,name);

9001 In2iGui.Window.prototype = {
9002 	addBehavior : function() {
9003 		var self = this;

9005 			this.close.observe('click',function(e) {
9006 				this.hide();
9007 				this.fire('userClosedWindow');

9009 			).observe('mousedown',function(e) {e.stop();});
9010 		}

9012 		this.titlebar.observe('touchstart',function(e) {self.startDrag(e);return false;});
9013 		this.element.observe('mousedown',function() {
9014 			self.element.style.zIndex=In2iGui.nextPanelIndex();
9015 		})
9016 	},

9018 		this.title.update(title);
9019 	},
9020 	show : function() {
9021 		if (this.visible) return;
9022 		this.element.setStyle({
9023 			zIndex : In2iGui.nextPanelIndex(), visibility : 'hidden', display : 'block', top: (n2i.getScrollTop()+40)+'px'
9024 		})
9025 		var width = this.element.clientWidth;
9026 		this.element.setStyle({
9027 			width : width+'px' , visibility : 'visible'
9028 		});
9029 		if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
9030 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,0);
9031 		}
9032 		this.visible = true;
9033 		In2iGui.callDescendants(this,'parentShown');
9034 	},

9036 		(this.visible ? this.hide() : this.show() );
9037 	},
9038 	hide : function() {
9039 		if (!this.visible) return;
9040 		if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
9041 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',0,200,{hideOnComplete:true});
9042 		} else {
9043 			this.element.setStyle({display:'none'});
9044 		}
9045 		this.visible = false;
9046 	},
9047 	add : function(widgetOrNode) {
9048 		if (widgetOrNode.getElement) {
9049 			this.content.insert(widgetOrNode.getElement());
9050 		} else {
9051 			this.content.insert(widgetOrNode);
9052 		}
9053 	},
9054 	setVariant : function(variant) {
9055 		this.element.removeClassName('in2igui_window_dark');
9056 		this.element.removeClassName('in2igui_window_light');

9058 			this.element.addClassName('in2igui_window_'+variant);
9059 		}

9062 ////////////////////////////// Dragging ////////////////////////////////
9063 
9064 	startDrag : function(e) {
9065 		var event = Event.extend(e || window.event);
9066 		this.element.style.zIndex=In2iGui.nextPanelIndex();
9067 		var pos = this.element.cumulativeOffset();
9068 		this.dragState = {left:event.pointerX()-pos.left,top:event.pointerY()-pos.top};
9069 		this.latestPosition = {left: this.dragState.left, top:this.dragState.top};
9070 		this.latestTime = new Date().getMilliseconds();
9071 		var self = this;
9072 		this.moveListener = function(e) {self.drag(e)};
9073 		this.upListener = function(e) {self.endDrag(e)};
9074 		Event.observe(document,'mousemove',this.moveListener);
9075 		Event.observe(document,'mouseup',this.upListener);
9076 		event.stop();
9077 		document.body.onselectstart = function () { return false; };
9078 		return false;
9079 	},
9080 	calc : function(top,left) {
9081 		// TODO: No need to do this all the time
9082 		this.a = this.latestPosition.left-left;
9083 		this.b = this.latestPosition.top-top;
9084 		this.dist = Math.sqrt(Math.pow((this.a),2),Math.pow((this.b),2));
9085 		this.latestTime = new Date().getMilliseconds();
9086 		this.latestPosition = {'top':top,'left':left};
9087 	},
9088 	drag : function(e) {
9089 		var event = Event.extend(e);
9090 		this.element.style.right = 'auto';
9091 		var top = (event.pointerY()-this.dragState.top);
9092 		var left = (event.pointerX()-this.dragState.left);
9093 		this.element.style.top = Math.max(top,0)+'px';
9094 		this.element.style.left = Math.max(left,0)+'px';
9095 		//this.calc(top,left);
9096 		return false;
9097 	},
9098 	endDrag : function(e) {
9099 		Event.stopObserving(document,'mousemove',this.moveListener);
9100 		Event.stopObserving(document,'mouseup',this.upListener);
9101 		document.body.onselectstart = null;
9102 	}
9103 }

9116 /** @static Creates a new formula */
9117 In2iGui.Formula.create = function(o) {
9118 	o = o || {};
9119 	o.element = new Element('form',{'class':'in2igui_formula'});
9120 	return new In2iGui.Formula(o);

9123 In2iGui.Formula.prototype = {
9124 	/** @private */
9125 	addBehavior : function() {
9126 		this.element.onsubmit=function() {
9127 			this.fire('submit');
9128 			return false
9129 		}.bind(this);
9130 	},
9131 	/** Returns a map of all values of descendants */
9132 	getValues : function() {
9133 		var data = {};
9134 		var d = In2iGui.get().getDescendants(this);
9135 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
9136 			if (d[i].options&& d[i].options.key && d[i].getValue) {
9137 				data[d[i].options.key] = d[i].getValue();
9138 			} else if (d[i].name && d[i].getValue) {
9139 				data[d[i].name] = d[i].getValue();
9140 			}
9141 		};
9142 		return data;
9143 	},
9144 	/** Returns a map of all values of descendants */
9145 	setValues : function(values) {
9146 		var d = In2iGui.get().getDescendants(this);
9147 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
9148 			if (d[i].options && d[i].options.key) {
9149 				var key = d[i].options.key;
9150 				if (key && values[key]) {
9151 					d[i].setValue(values[key]);
9152 				}
9153 			}
9154 		}
9155 	},
9156 	/** Resets all descendants */
9157 	reset : function() {
9158 		var d = In2iGui.get().getDescendants(this);
9159 		for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
9160 			if (d[i].reset) d[i].reset();
9161 		}
9162 	},
9163 	/** Adds a widget to the form */
9164 	add : function(widget) {
9165 		this.element.insert(widget.getElement());
9166 	},
9167 	/** Creates a new form group and adds it to the form
9168 	 * @returns {'In2iGui.Formula.Group'} group
9169 	 */
9170 	createGroup : function(options) {
9171 		var g = In2iGui.Formula.Group.create(null,options);
9172 		this.add(g);
9173 		return g;
9174 	},
9175 	/** Builds and adds a new group according to a recipe */
9176 	buildGroup : function(options,recipe) {
9177 		var g = this.createGroup(options);
9178 		recipe.each(function(item) {
9179 			var w = In2iGui.Formula[item.type].create(null,item.options);
9180 			g.add(w);
9181 		});
9182 	},
9183 	/** @private */
9184 	childValueChanged : function(value) {
9185 		this.fire('valuesChanged',this.getValues());
9186 	}
9187 }

9286 		}
9287 	},

9295 	},

9314 /********************** Dat time ***********************/
9315 
9316 In2iGui.Formula.DateTime = function(o) {
9317 	this.inputFormats = ['d-m-Y','d/m-Y','d/m/Y','d-m-Y H:i:s','d/m-Y H:i:s','d/m/Y H:i:s','d-m-Y H:i','d/m-Y H:i','d/m/Y H:i','d-m-Y H','d/m-Y H','d/m/Y H','d-m','d/m','d','Y','m-d-Y','m-d','m/d'];
9318 	this.outputFormat = 'd-m-Y H:i:s';
9319 	this.name = o.name;
9320 	this.element = $(o.element);
9321 	this.input = this.element.select('input')[0];
9322 	this.options = n2i.override({returnType:null,label:null},o);
9323 	this.value = null;
9324 	In2iGui.extend(this);
9325 	this.addBehavior();
9326 }
9327 
9328 In2iGui.Formula.DateTime.prototype = {
9329 	addBehavior : function() {
9330 		In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:this.input,classElement:this.element,'class':'in2igui_field_focused'});
9331 		this.input.observe('blur',this.check.bind(this));
9332 	},
9333 	updateFromNode : function(node) {
9334 		if (node.firstChild) {
9335 			this.setValue(node.firstChild.nodeValue);
9336 		} else {
9337 			this.setValue(null);
9338 		}
9339 	},
9340 	updateFromObject : function(data) {
9341 		this.setValue(data.value);
9342 	},
9343 	focus : function() {
9344 		try {this.input.focus();} catch (ignore) {}
9345 	},
9346 	reset : function() {
9347 		this.setValue('');
9348 	},
9349 	setValue : function(value) {
9350 		if (!value) {
9351 			this.value = null;
9352 		} else if (value.constructor==Date) {
9353 			this.value = value;
9354 		} else {
9355 			this.value = new Date();
9356 			this.value.setTime(parseInt(value)*1000);
9357 		}
9358 		this.updateUI();
9359 	},
9360 	check : function() {
9361 		var str = this.input.value;
9362 		var parsed = null;
9363 		for (var i=0; i < this.inputFormats.length && parsed==null; i++) {
9364 			parsed = Date.parseDate(str,this.inputFormats[i]);
9365 		};
9366 		this.value = parsed;
9367 		this.updateUI();
9368 	},
9369 	getValue : function() {
9370 		if (this.value!=null && this.options.returnType=='seconds') {
9371 			return Math.round(this.value.getTime()/1000);
9372 		}
9373 		return this.value;
9374 	},
9375 	getElement : function() {
9376 		return this.element;
9377 	},
9378 	getLabel : function() {
9379 		return this.options.label;
9380 	},
9381 	updateUI : function() {
9382 		if (this.value) {
9383 			this.input.value = this.value.dateFormat(this.outputFormat);
9384 		} else {
9385 			this.input.value = ''
9386 		}
9387 	}
9388 }

9392 In2iGui.Formula.DropDown = function(o) {

9397 	this.items = o.items || [];
9398 	this.index = -1;
9399 	this.value = this.options.value || null;
9400 	this.dirty = true;
9401 	In2iGui.extend(this);
9402 	this.addBehavior();
9403 	this.updateIndex();
9404 	this.updateUI();
9405 	if (this.options.url) {
9406 		this.options.source = new In2iGui.Source({url:this.options.url,delegate:this});
9407 	} else if (this.options.source) {
9408 		this.options.source.addDelegate(this);	
9409 	}
9410 }

9413 	o = o || {};

9415 		'<span><span><strong></strong></span></span>'
9416 	);

9419 
9420 In2iGui.Formula.DropDown.prototype = {
9421 	addBehavior : function() {
9422 		In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:this.element,'class':'in2igui_dropdown_focused'});
9423 		this.element.observe('click',this.clicked.bind(this));
9424 		this.element.observe('blur',this.hideSelector.bind(this));
9425 	},
9426 	updateIndex : function() {
9427 		this.items.each(function(item,i) {
9428 			if (item.value==this.value) this.index=i;
9429 		}.bind(this));
9430 	},
9431 	updateUI : function() {
9432 		if (this.items[this.index]) {
9433 			this.inner.update(this.items[this.index].title);
9434 		}
9435 		if (!this.selector) return;
9436 		this.selector.select('a').each(function(a,i) {
9437 			if (this.index==i) {
9438 				a.addClassName('in2igui_selected');
9439 			}
9440 			else a.className='';
9441 		}.bind(this));
9442 	},
9443 	clicked : function(e) {
9444 		e.stop();
9445 		this.buildSelector();
9446 		var el = this.element,s=this.selector;
9447 		el.focus();
9448 		if (!this.items) return;
9449 		In2iGui.positionAtElement(s,el,{vertical:'bottomOutside',top:-2,left:2});
9450 		s.setStyle({display:'block',width:(el.getWidth()-5)+'px',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex()});
9451 	},
9452 	getValue : function(value) {
9453 		return this.value;
9454 	},
9455 	getLabel : function() {
9456 		return this.options.label;
9457 	},
9458 	refresh : function() {
9459 		if (this.options.source) {
9460 			this.options.source.refresh();
9461 		}
9462 	},
9463 	addItem : function(item) {
9464 		this.items.push(item);
9465 		this.dirty = true;
9466 		this.updateIndex();
9467 		this.updateUI();
9468 	},
9469 	setItems : function(items) {
9470 		this.items = items;
9471 		this.dirty = true;
9472 		this.index = -1;
9473 		this.updateIndex();
9474 		this.updateUI();
9475 	},
9476 	itemsLoaded : function(items) {
9477 		this.setItems(items);
9478 	},
9479 	hideSelector : function() {
9480 		if (!this.selector) return;
9481 		this.selector.hide();
9482 	},
9483 	buildSelector : function() {
9484 		if (!this.dirty || !this.items) return;
9485 		if (!this.selector) {
9486 			this.selector = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_dropdown_selector'});
9487 			document.body.appendChild(this.selector);
9488 		} else {
9489 			this.selector.update();
9490 		}
9491 		var self = this;
9492 		this.items.each(function(item,i) {
9493 			var e = new Element('a',{href:'#'}).update(item.title).observe('mousedown',function(e) {
9494 				e.stop();
9495 				self.itemClicked(item,i);
9496 			})
9497 			if (i==self.index) e.addClassName('in2igui_selected');
9498 			self.selector.insert(e);
9499 		});
9500 		this.dirty = false;
9501 	},
9502 	itemClicked : function(item,index) {
9503 		this.index = index;
9504 		this.value = this.items[index].value;
9505 		this.updateUI();
9506 		this.hideSelector();
9507 	}
9508 }

9512 In2iGui.Formula.Select = function(id,name,options) {
9513 	this.name = name;
9514 	this.options = n2i.override({label:null},options);
9515 	this.element = $(id);
9516 	this.value = this.options.value || null;
9517 	this.invalidValue = false;
9518 	In2iGui.extend(this);
9519 	this.addBehavior();
9520 	this.refresh();
9521 }
9522 
9523 In2iGui.Formula.Select.create = function(name,options) {
9524 	var e = new Element('select');
9525 	return new In2iGui.Formula.Select(e,name,options);
9526 }
9527 
9528 In2iGui.Formula.Select.prototype = {
9529 	addBehavior : function() {
9530 		var self = this;
9531 		this.element.observe('change',function() {
9532 			self.valueMightChange();
9533 		});
9534 	},
9535 	refresh : function() {
9536 		if (this.options.source) {
9537 			var self = this;
9538 			new Ajax.Request(this.options.source, {onSuccess: function(t) {self.update(t.responseXML)}});
9539 		}
9540 	},
9541 	update : function(doc) {
9542 		for (var i = this.element.options.length - 1; i >= 0; i--){
9543 			this.element.remove(i);
9544 		};
9545 		var items = doc.getElementsByTagName('item');
9546 		for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
9547 			var title = items[i].getAttribute('title');
9548 			var value = items[i].getAttribute('value');
9549 			this.element.options[this.element.options.length] = new Option(title,value);
9550 		};
9551 		this.setValue(this.value);
9552 	},
9553 	valueMightChange : function() {
9554 		if (this.element.value!=this.value) {
9555 			this.value=this.element.value;
9556 			In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'valueDidChange',this.value);
9557 		}
9558 	},
9559 	reset : function() {
9560 		this.element.selectedIndex = 0;
9561 		this.value = null;
9562 	},
9563 	setValue : function(value) {
9564 		value=value+'';
9565 		for (var i=0; i < this.element.options.length; i++) {
9566 			if (this.element.options[i].value==value) {
9567 				this.element.selectedIndex = i;
9568 				this.value = value;
9569 				if (this.invalidValue) {
9570 					this.element.firstDescendant().remove();
9571 				}
9572 				return;
9573 			}
9574 		};
9575 		if (this.invalidValue) {
9576 			this.element.firstDescendant().value=value;
9577 		} else {
9578 			this.element.insert({top:new Element('option',{value:value})});
9579 			this.invalidValue = true;
9580 		}
9581 		this.element.selectedIndex=0;
9582 		this.value = value;
9583 	},
9584 	getValue : function(value) {
9585 		return this.element.value;
9586 	},
9587 	getLabel : function() {
9588 		return this.options.label;
9589 	}
9590 }

9677 In2iGui.Formula.Checkboxes = function(id,name,options) {

9865 		this.element.insert(input);
9866 		var self = this;

9930 	},

9932 		if (this.options.source!=source) {
9933 			this.options.source.removeDelegate(this);
9934 			source.addDelegate(this);
9935 			this.options.source = source;
9936 			source.refresh();
9937 		}
9938 	},
9939 	setUrl : function(url) {
9940 		this.url = url;
9941 		this.selected = [];
9942 		this.sortKey = null;
9943 		this.sortDirection = null;
9944 		this.window.page = 0;
9945 		this.refresh();
9946 	},
9947 	resetState : function() {
9948 		this.window = {size:null,page:0,total:0};
9949 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'state',this.window);
9950 	},
9951 	valueForProperty : function(p) {
9952 		if (p=='window.page') return this.window.page;
9953 		else if (p=='sort.key') return this.sortKey;
9954 		else if (p=='sort.direction') return (this.sortDirection || 'ascending');
9955 		else return this[p];
9956 	},
9957 	/**
9958 	 * @private
9959 	 */
9960 	refresh : function() {
9961 		if (this.options.source) {
9962 			this.options.source.refresh();
9963 			return;
9964 		}
9965 		if (!this.url) return;
9966 		var url = this.url;
9967 		if (typeof(this.window.page)=='number') {
9968 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
9969 			url+='windowPage='+this.window.page;
9970 		}
9971 		if (this.window.size) {
9972 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
9973 			url+='windowSize='+this.window.size;
9974 		}
9975 		if (this.sortKey) {
9976 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
9977 			url+='sort='+this.sortKey;
9978 		}
9979 		if (this.sortDirection) {
9980 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
9981 			url+='direction='+this.sortDirection;
9982 		}
9983 		for (key in this.parameters) {
9984 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
9985 			url+=key+'='+this.parameters[key];
9986 		}
9987 		var self = this;
9988 		new Ajax.Request(url,{
9989 			onSuccess:function(r) {
9990 				if (r.responseXML) {
9991 					try {
9992 					self.listLoaded(r.responseXML);
9993 					} catch (e) {n2i.log(e)}
9994 				} else if (r.responseText) {
9995 					var json = r.responseText.evalJSON();
9996 					if (json.list==true) {
9997 						self.setData(json);
9998 					} else {
9999 						self.setObjects(json);
10000 					}
10001 				}
10002 			}
10003 		});
10004 	},
10005 	sort : function(index) {
10006 		var key = this.columns[index].key;
10007 		if (key==this.sortKey) {
10008 			this.sortDirection = this.sortDirection=='ascending' ? 'descending' : 'ascending';
10009 			In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'sort.direction',this.sortDirection);
10010 		} else {
10011 			In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'sort.key',key);
10012 		}
10013 		this.sortKey = key;
10014 		this.refresh();
10015 	},
10016 
10017 	/**
10018 	 * @private
10019 	 */
10020 	listLoaded : function(doc) {
10021 		this.parseWindow(doc);
10022 		this.buildNavigation();
10023 		this.body.update();
10024 		this.head.update();
10025 		this.rows = [];
10026 		this.columns = [];
10027 		var headTr = new Element('tr');
10028 		var sort = doc.getElementsByTagName('sort');
10029 		this.sortKey=null;
10030 		this.sortDirection=null;
10031 		if (sort.length>0) {
10032 			this.sortKey=sort[0].getAttribute('key');
10033 			this.sortDirection=sort[0].getAttribute('direction');
10034 		}
10035 		var headers = doc.getElementsByTagName('header');
10036 		for (var i=0; i < headers.length; i++) {
10037 			var className = '';
10038 			var th = new Element('th');
10039 			var width = headers[i].getAttribute('width');
10040 			var key = headers[i].getAttribute('key');
10041 			var sortable = headers[i].getAttribute('sortable')=='true';
10042 			if (width && width!='') {
10043 				th.style.width=width+'%';
10044 			}
10045 			if (sortable) {
10046 				var self = this;
10047 				th.in2iguiIndex = i;
10048 				th.onclick=function() {self.sort(this.in2iguiIndex)};
10049 				className+='sortable';
10050 			}
10051 			if (key==this.sortKey) {
10052 				className+=' sort_'+this.sortDirection;
10053 			}
10054 			th.className=className;
10055 			var span = new Element('span');
10056 			th.appendChild(span);
10057 			span.appendChild(document.createTextNode(headers[i].getAttribute('title')));
10058 			headTr.appendChild(th);
10059 			this.columns.push({'key':key,'sortable':sortable,'width':width});
10060 		};
10061 		this.head.appendChild(headTr);
10062 		var rows = doc.getElementsByTagName('row');
10063 		for (var i=0; i < rows.length; i++) {
10064 			var cells = rows[i].getElementsByTagName('cell');
10065 			var row = new Element('tr');
10066 			var icon = rows[i].getAttribute('icon');
10067 			var title = rows[i].getAttribute('title');
10068 			for (var j=0; j < cells.length; j++) {
10069 				var td = new Element('td');
10070 				this.parseCell(cells[j],td);
10071 				row.insert(td);
10072 				if (!title) title = cells[j].innerText;
10073 				if (!icon && cells[j].getAttribute('icon')) icon = cells[j].getAttribute('icon');
10074 			};
10075 			var info = {id:rows[i].getAttribute('id'),kind:rows[i].getAttribute('kind'),icon:icon,title:title,index:i};
10076 			row.dragDropInfo = info;
10077 			this.addRowBehavior(row,i);
10078 			this.body.insert(row);
10079 			this.rows.push(info);
10080 		};
10081 	},

10098 In2iGui.List.prototype.filter = function(str) {
10099 	var len = 20;
10100 	var regex = new RegExp("[\\w]{"+len+",}","g");
10101 	var match = regex.exec(str);
10102 	if (match) {
10103 		for (var i=0; i < match.length; i++) {
10104 			var rep = '';
10105 			for (var j=0; j < match[i].length; j++) {
10106 				rep+=match[i][j];
10107 				if ((j+1)%len==0) rep+='\u200B';
10108 			};
10109 			str = str.replace(match[i],rep);
10110 		};
10111 	}
10112 	return str;
10113 }
10114 
10115 In2iGui.List.prototype.parseCell = function(node,cell) {
10116 	if (node.getAttribute('icon')!=null) {
10117 		var icon = new Element('div',{'class':'icon'}).setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url("'+In2iGui.getIconUrl(node.getAttribute('icon'),1)+'")'});
10118 		cell.insert(icon);
10119 	}
10120 	for (var i=0; i < node.childNodes.length; i++) {
10121 		var child = node.childNodes[i];
10122 		if (child.nodeType==n2i.TEXT_NODE && child.nodeValue.length>0) {
10123 			cell.appendChild(document.createTextNode(child.nodeValue));
10124 		} else if (child.nodeType==n2i.ELEMENT_NODE && child.nodeName=='break') {
10125 			cell.insert(new Element('br'));
10126 		} else if (child.nodeType==n2i.ELEMENT_NODE && child.nodeName=='object') {
10127 			var obj = new Element('div',{'class':'object'});
10128 			if (child.getAttribute('icon')!=null) {
10129 				var icon = new Element('div',{'class':'icon'}).setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url("'+In2iGui.getIconUrl(child.getAttribute('icon'),1)+'")'});
10130 				obj.insert(icon);
10131 			}
10132 			if (child.firstChild && child.firstChild.nodeType==n2i.TEXT_NODE && child.firstChild.nodeValue.length>0) {
10133 				obj.appendChild(document.createTextNode(child.firstChild.nodeValue));
10134 			}
10135 			cell.insert(obj);
10136 		}
10137 	};
10138 }

10140 /**
10141  * @private
10142  */
10143 In2iGui.List.prototype.parseWindow = function(doc) {
10144 	var wins = doc.getElementsByTagName('window');
10145 	if (wins.length>0) {
10146 		var win = wins[0];
10147 		this.window.total = parseInt(win.getAttribute('total'));
10148 		this.window.size = parseInt(win.getAttribute('size'));
10149 		this.window.page = parseInt(win.getAttribute('page'));
10150 	} else {
10151 		this.window.total = 0;
10152 		this.window.size = 0;
10153 		this.window.page = 0;
10154 	}
10155 }

10157 In2iGui.List.prototype.buildNavigation = function() {
10158 	var self = this;
10159 	var pages = this.window.size>0 ? Math.ceil(this.window.total/this.window.size) : 0;
10160 	if (pages<2) {
10161 		this.navigation.style.display='none';
10162 		return;
10163 	}
10164 	this.navigation.style.display='block';
10165 	var from = ((this.window.page)*this.window.size+1);
10166 	this.count.update('<span><span>'+from+'-'+Math.min((this.window.page+1)*this.window.size,this.window.total)+'/'+this.window.total+'</span></span>');
10167 	this.windowPageBody.update();
10168 	if (pages<2) {
10169 		this.windowPage.style.display='none';	
10170 	} else {
10171 		for (var i=0;i<pages;i++) {
10172 			var a = document.createElement('a');
10173 			a.appendChild(document.createTextNode(i+1));
10174 			a.in2GuiPage = i;
10175 			a.onclick = function() {
10176 				self.windowPageWasClicked(this);
10177 				return false;
10178 			}
10179 			if (i==this.window.page) {
10180 				a.className='selected';
10181 			}
10182 			this.windowPageBody.appendChild(a);
10183 		}
10184 		this.windowPage.style.display='block';
10185 	}
10186 }

10201 In2iGui.List.prototype.buildHeaders = function(headers) {

10221 In2iGui.List.prototype.buildRows = function(rows) {
10222 	var self = this;
10223 	this.body.update();
10224 	//this.body = new Element('tbody');
10225 	this.rows = [];
10226 	if (!rows) return;
10227 	rows.each(function(r,i) {
10228 		var tr = new Element('tr');
10229 		var icon = r.icon;
10230 		var title = r.title;
10231 		r.cells.each(function(c) {
10232 			var td = new Element('td');
10233 			if (c.icon) {
10234 				var icn = new Element('div',{'class':'icon'}).setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url("'+In2iGui.getIconUrl(c.icon,1)+'")'});
10235 				td.insert(icn);
10236 				icon = icon || c.icon;
10237 			}
10238 			if (c.text) {
10239 				td.insert(c.text);
10240 				title = title || c.text;
10241 			}
10242 			tr.insert(td);
10243 		})
10244 		self.body.insert(tr);
10245 		var info = {id:r.id,kind:r.kind,icon:icon,title:title,index:i};
10246 		tr.dragDropInfo = info;
10247 		self.addRowBehavior(tr,i);
10248 		self.rows.push(info);
10249 	})

10256 In2iGui.List.prototype.setObjects = function(objects) {
10257 	this.selected = [];
10258 	this.body.update();
10259 	this.rows = [];
10260 	for (var i=0; i < objects.length; i++) {
10261 		var row = new Element('tr');
10262 		var obj = objects[i];
10263 		for (var j=0; j < this.columns.length; j++) {
10264 			var cell = new Element('td');
10265 			if (this.builder) {
10266 				cell.update(this.builder.buildColumn(this.columns[j],obj));
10267 			} else {
10268 				var value = obj[this.columns[j].key] || '';
10269 				if (value.constructor == Array) {
10270 					for (var k=0; k < value.length; k++) {
10271 						if (value[k].constructor == Object) {
10272 							cell.insert(this.createObject(value[k]));
10273 						} else {
10274 							cell.insert(new Element('div').update(value));
10275 						}
10276 					};
10277 				} else if (value.constructor == Object) {
10278 					cell.insert(this.createObject(value[j]));
10279 				} else {
10280 					cell.insert(value);
10281 				}
10282 			}
10283 			row.insert(cell);
10284 		};
10285 		this.body.insert(row);
10286 		this.addRowBehavior(row,i);
10287 		this.rows.push(obj);
10288 	};
10289 }
10290 
10291 In2iGui.List.prototype.createObject = function(object) {
10292 	var node = new Element('div',{'class':'object'});
10293 	if (object.icon) {
10294 		node.insert(new Element('div',{'class':'icon'}).setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url("'+In2iGui.getIconUrl(object.icon,1)+'")'}));
10295 	}
10296 	return node.insert(object.text || object.name || '');
10297 }

10429 In2iGui.ObjectList.prototype = {
10430 	ignite : function() {
10431 		this.addObject({});
10432 	},
10433 	addObject : function(data,addToEnd) {
10434 		if (this.objects.length==0 || addToEnd) {
10435 			var obj = new In2iGui.ObjectList.Object(this.objects.length,data,this);
10436 			this.objects.push(obj);
10437 			this.body.appendChild(obj.getElement());
10438 		} else {
10439 			var last = this.objects.pop();
10440 			var obj = new In2iGui.ObjectList.Object(last.index,data,this);
10441 			last.index++;
10442 			this.objects.push(obj);
10443 			this.objects.push(last);
10444 			this.body.insertBefore(obj.getElement(),last.getElement())
10445 		}
10446 	},
10447 	reset : function() {
10448 		for (var i=0; i < this.objects.length; i++) {
10449 			var element = this.objects[i].getElement();
10450 			element.parentNode.removeChild(element);
10451 		};
10452 		this.objects = [];
10453 		this.addObject({});
10454 	},
10455 	addObjects : function(data) {
10456 		for (var i=0; i < data.length; i++) {
10457 			this.addObject(data[i]);
10458 		};
10459 	},
10460 	setObjects : function(data) {
10461 		this.reset();
10462 		this.addObjects(data);
10463 	},
10464 	getObjects : function(data) {
10465 		var list = [];
10466 		for (var i=0; i < this.objects.length-1; i++) {
10467 			list.push(this.objects[i].getData());
10468 		};
10469 		return list;
10470 	},
10471 	getValue : function() {
10472 		return this.getObjects();
10473 	},
10474 	setValue : function(data) {
10475 		this.setObjects(data);
10476 	},
10477 	registerTemplateItem : function(item) {
10478 		this.template.push(item);
10479 	},
10480 	objectDidChange : function(obj) {
10481 		if (obj.index>=this.objects.length-1) {
10482 			this.addObject({},true);
10483 		}
10484 	}
10485 }

10496 In2iGui.ObjectList.Object.prototype = {

10498 		if (!this.element) {
10499 			var self = this;
10500 			this.element = document.createElement('tr');
10501 			for (var i=0; i < this.list.template.length; i++) {
10502 				var template = this.list.template[i];
10503 				var field = template.clone();
10504 				field.object = this;
10505 				this.fields.push(field);
10506 				var cell = document.createElement('td');
10507 				if (i==0) cell.className='first';
10508 				cell.appendChild(field.getElement());
10509 				field.setValue(this.data[template.key]);
10510 				this.element.appendChild(cell);
10511 			};
10512 		}
10513 		return this.element;
10514 	},
10515 	valueDidChange : function() {
10516 		this.list.objectDidChange(this);
10517 	},

10520 		for (var i=0; i < this.fields.length; i++) {
10521 			data[this.fields[i].key] = this.fields[i].getValue();
10522 		};
10523 		return data;
10524 	}
