10610 /**
10611  * Creates a new instance of an alert
10612  * @static
10613  */
10614 In2iGui.Alert.create = function(name,options) {
10615 	options = n2i.override({title:'',text:'',emotion:null,variant:null,title:null},options);
10616 	
10617 	var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_alert'});
10618 	var body = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_alert_body'});
10619 	element.insert(body);
10620 	var content = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_alert_content'});
10621 	body.insert(content);
10622 	document.body.appendChild(element);
10623 	var obj = new In2iGui.Alert(element,name,options);
10624 	if (options.variant) {
10625 		obj.setVariant(options.variant);
10626 	}
10627 	if (options.emotion) {
10628 		obj.setEmotion(options.emotion);
10629 	}
10630 	if (options.title) {
10631 		obj.setTitle(options.title);
10632 	}
10633 	if (options.text) {
10634 		obj.setText(options.text);
10635 	}
10636 	
10637 	return obj;
10638 }

10708 In2iGui.Button.create = function(name,o) {

10710 	var className = 'in2igui_button'+(o.highlighted ? ' in2igui_button_highlighted' : '');
10711 	if (!o.enabled) className+=' in2igui_button_disabled';
10712 	var element = new Element('a',{'class':className,href:'#'});
10713 	var element2 = new Element('span');
10714 	element.appendChild(element2);
10715 	var element3 = new Element('span');
10716 	element2.appendChild(element3);
10717 	if (o.icon) {

10719 		if (!o.text || o.text.length==0) {
10720 			icon.addClassName('in2igui_button_icon_notext');
10721 		}
10722 		element3.insert(icon);
10723 	}
10724 	if (o.text && o.text.length>0) {
10725 		element3.insert(o.text);
10726 	}
10727 	if (o.title && o.title.length>0) {
10728 		element3.insert(o.title);
10729 	}
10730 	return new In2iGui.Button(element,name);
10731 }

10802 
10803 In2iGui.Selection.prototype = {
10804 	getValue : function() {
10805 		return this.value;
10806 	},
10807 	getSelection : function() {
10808 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
10809 			if (this.items[i].value == this.value) {
10810 				return this.items[i];
10811 			}
10812 		};
10813 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
10814 			var item = this.subItems[i].getSelection();
10815 			if (item) return item;
10816 		};
10817 	},
10818 	setValue : function(value) {
10819 		this.value = value;
10820 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
10821 			var item = this.items[i];
10822 			item.element.setClassName('selected',(item.value==value));
10823 		};
10824 		this.subItems.each(function(sub) {
10825 			sub.updateUI();
10826 		});
10827 	},
10828 	changeValue : function(value) {
10829 		this.setValue(value);
10830 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectorSelectionChanged'); // deprecated
10831 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectionChanged',this.value); // deprecated
10832 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'onSelectionChange',this.value);
10833 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'value',this.value);
10834 	},
10835 	registerItems : function(items) {
10836 		items.selection = this;
10837 		this.subItems.push(items);
10838 	},
10839 	registerItem : function(id,title,icon,badge,value,kind) {
10840 		var element = $(id);
10841 		element.in2iGuiValue = value;
10842 		this.items.push({id:id,title:title,icon:icon,badge:badge,element:element,value:value,kind:kind});
10843 		var self = this;
10844 		element.onclick = function() {
10845 			self.itemWasClicked(value);
10846 		}
10847 		element.ondblclick = function() {
10848 			self.itemWasDoubleClicked();
10849 			return false;
10850 		}
10851 		element.dragDropInfo = {kind:kind,value:value};
10852 		element.addClassName('droppable');
10853 		element.observe('mouseover',In2iGui.dropOverListener);
10854 		element.observe('mouseout',In2iGui.dropOutListener);
10855 	},
10856 	
10857 	setObjects : function(items) {
10858 		var self = this;
10859 		items.each(function(item) {
10860 			self.items.push(item);
10861 			var node = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_item'});
10862 			item.element = node;
10863 			self.element.insert(node);
10864 			var inner = new Element('span').update(item.title);
10865 			if (item.icon) {
10866 				inner.setStyle({'backgroundImage' : 'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(item.icon,1)+')'}).addClassName('in2igui_icon');
10867 			}
10868 			node.insert(inner);
10869 			node.observe('click',function() {
10870 				self.changeValue(item.value);
10871 			});
10872 			node.observe('dblclick',function() {
10873 				self.itemWasDoubleClicked();
10874 				return false;
10875 			});
10876 		});
10877 	},
10878 	
10879 	// Events
10880 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
10881 		this.changeValue(value);
10882 	},
10883 	itemWasDoubleClicked : function() {
10884 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectorObjectWasOpened');
10885 	}
10886 }

10890 In2iGui.Selection.Items = function(id,name,options) {
10891 	this.element = $(id);
10892 	this.name = name;
10893 	this.value = null;
10894 	this.selection = null;
10895 	this.options = n2i.override({source:null},options);
10896 	this.items = [];
10897 	In2iGui.extend(this);
10898 	var self = this;
10899 	if (this.options.source) {
10900 		this.options.source.addDelegate(this);
10901 	}

10903 
10904 In2iGui.Selection.Items.prototype = {
10905 	refresh : function() {
10906 		if (this.options.source) {
10907 			this.options.source.refresh();
10908 		}
10909 	},
10910 	objectsLoaded : function(objects) {
10911 		this.itemsLoaded(objects);
10912 	},
10913 	itemsLoaded : function(items) {
10914 		this.items = [];
10915 		this.element.update();
10916 		var self = this;
10917 		for (var i=0, len=items.length; i < len; ++i) {
10918 			var item = items[i];
10919 			var node = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_item'});
10920 			var inner = new Element('span');
10921 			if (item.icon) {
10922 				inner.setStyle({'backgroundImage' : 'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(item.icon,1)+')'}).addClassName('in2igui_icon');
10923 			}
10924 			node.in2iGuiIndex = i;
10925 			node.insert(inner.insert(item.title));
10926 			this.element.insert(node);
10927 			node.observe('click',function() {
10928 				self.itemWasClicked(self.items[this.in2iGuiIndex].value);
10929 			});
10930 			node.ondblclick = function() {
10931 				self.itemWasDoubleClicked();
10932 				return false;
10933 			}
10934 			var info = {title:item.title,icon:item.icon,badge:item.badge,kind:item.kind,element:node,value:item.value};
10935 			node.dragDropInfo = info;
10936 			this.items.push(info);
10937 		};
10938 		this.updateUI();
10939 	},
10940 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
10941 		this.selection.changeValue(value);
10942 	},
10943 	itemWasDoubleClicked : function(node) {
10944 		this.selection.itemWasDoubleClicked();
10945 	},
10946 	getSelection : function() {
10947 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
10948 			if (this.items[i].value == this.selection.value) {
10949 				return this.items[i];
10950 			}
10951 		};
10952 		return null;
10953 	},
10954 	updateUI : function() {
10955 		var newValue = null;
10956 		this.items.each(function(item) {
10957 			if (item.value==this.selection.value) newValue=item.value;
10958 			item.element.setClassName('selected',(item.value==this.selection.value));
10959 		}.bind(this));
10960 		if (this.value!=newValue) {
10961 			this.value=newValue;
10962 			In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'value',this.value);
10963 		}
10964 	}
10965 }

11187 			remove.addDelegate({
11188 				click:function() {self.setObject(null);self.hidePicker()}
11189 			});

11191 			buttons.appendChild(remove.getElement());

11193 			this.picker.add(buttons);
11194 		}

11210 			}
11211 		};

11222 			thumb.in2iguiObject = {'id':id};

11265 In2iGui.BoundPanel.prototype = {
11266 	show : function() {
11267 		if (!this.visible) {
11268 			if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
11269 				n2i.setOpacity(this.element,0);
11270 			}
11271 			if (this.relativePosition=='left') {
11272 				this.element.style.marginLeft='30px';
11273 			} else {
11274 				this.element.style.marginLeft='-30px';
11275 			}
11276 			this.element.setStyle({
11277 				visibility : 'hidden', display : 'block'
11278 			})
11279 			var width = this.element.clientWidth;
11280 			this.element.setStyle({
11281 				width : width+'px' , visibility : 'visible'
11282 			});
11283 			this.element.style.marginTop='0px';
11284 			this.element.style.display='block';
11285 			if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
11286 				n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,400,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
11287 			}
11288 			n2i.ani(this.element,'margin-left','0px',800,{ease:n2i.ease.bounce});
11289 		}
11290 		this.element.style.zIndex = In2iGui.nextPanelIndex();
11291 		this.visible=true;
11292 	},
11293 	hide : function() {
11294 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {
11295 			this.element.style.display='none';
11296 		} else {
11297 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',0,300,{ease:n2i.ease.slowFast,hideOnComplete:true});
11298 		}
11299 		this.visible=false;
11300 	},
11301 	add : function(obj) {
11302 		if (obj.getElement) {
11303 			this.content.appendChild(obj.getElement());
11304 		} else {
11305 			this.content.appendChild(obj);
11306 		}
11307 	},
11308 	addSpace : function(height) {
11309 		this.add(new Element('div').setStyle({fontSize:'0px',height:height+'px'}));
11310 	},
11311 	getDimensions : function() {
11312 		if (this.element.style.display=='none') {
11313 			this.element.style.visibility='hidden';
11314 			this.element.style.display='block';
11315 			var width = this.element.getWidth();
11316 			var height = this.element.getHeight();
11317 			this.element.style.display='none';
11318 			this.element.style.visibility='';
11319 		} else {
11320 			var width = this.element.getWidth();
11321 			var height = this.element.getHeight();
11322 		}
11323 		return {width:width,height:height};
11324 	},
11325 	position : function(node) {
11326 		node = $(node);
11327 		var offset = node.cumulativeOffset();
11328 		var scrollOffset = node.cumulativeScrollOffset();
11329 		var dims = this.getDimensions();
11330 		var winWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth();
11331 		var nodeLeft = offset.left-scrollOffset.left+n2i.getScrollLeft();
11332 		var nodeWidth = node.getWidth();
11333 		var nodeHeight = node.getHeight();
11334 		var nodeTop = offset.top-scrollOffset.top+n2i.getScrollTop();
11335 		if ((nodeLeft+nodeWidth/2)/winWidth<.5) {
11336 			this.relativePosition='left';
11337 			var left = nodeLeft+nodeWidth+10;
11338 			this.arrow.className='arrow arrow_left';
11339 			var arrowLeft=-14;
11340 		} else {
11341 			this.relativePosition='right';
11342 			var left = nodeLeft-dims.width-10;
11343 			this.arrow.className='arrow arrow_right';
11344 			var arrowLeft=dims.width-4;
11345 		}
11346 		var top = Math.max(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2);
11347 		this.arrow.style.marginTop = (dims.height-32)/2+Math.min(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2)+'px';
11348 		this.arrow.style.marginLeft = arrowLeft+'px';
11349 		if (this.visible) {
11350 			n2i.ani(this.element,'top',top+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
11351 			n2i.ani(this.element,'left',left+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
11352 		} else {
11353 			this.element.style.top=top+'px';
11354 			this.element.style.left=left+'px';
11355 		}
11356 	}
11357 }

11400 In2iGui.RichText.replaceInput = function(options) {

11405 	input.parentNode.insertBefore(obj.element,input);
11406 	obj.ignite();

11423 		this.editor.observe("wysihat:loaded", function(event) {

11432 				this.document.documentElement.style.minHeight='100%';

11435 			Event.observe(this.window,'focus',function() {self.documentFocused()});
11436 			Event.observe(this.window,'blur',function() {self.documentBlurred()});
11437 			this.ignited = true;
11438      	}.bind(this));

11632 In2iGui.ImageViewer.prototype = {
11633 	addBehavior : function() {
11634 		var self = this;
11635 		this.nextControl.onclick = function() {
11636 			self.next(true);
11637 		}
11638 		this.previousControl.onclick = function() {
11639 			self.previous(true);
11640 		}
11641 		this.playControl.onclick = function() {
11642 			self.playOrPause();
11643 		}
11644 		this.viewer.onclick = function() {
11645 			self.hide();
11646 		}
11647 		this.timer = function() {
11648 			self.next(false);
11649 		}
11650 		this.keyListener = function(e) {
11651 			if (n2i.isRightKey(e)) {
11652 				self.next(true);
11653 			} else if (n2i.isLeftKey(e)) {
11654 				self.previous(true);
11655 			} else if (n2i.isEscapeKey(e)) {
11656 				self.hide();
11657 			} else if (n2i.isReturnKey(e)) {
11658 				self.playOrPause();
11659 			}
11660 		}
11661 	},
11662 	getLargestSize : function(canvas,image) {
11663 		if (image.width<=canvas.width && image.height<=canvas.height) {
11664 			return {width:image.width,height:image.height};
11665 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height>image.width/image.height) {
11666 			return {width:canvas.height/image.height*image.width,height:canvas.height};
11667 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height<image.width/image.height) {
11668 			return {width:canvas.width,height:canvas.width/image.width*image.height};
11669 		} else {
11670 			return {width:canvas.width,height:canvas.height};
11671 		}
11672 	},	
11673 	calculateSize : function() {
11674 		var snap = this.options.sizeSnap;
11675 		var newWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth()-this.options.perimeter;
11676 		newWidth = Math.floor(newWidth/snap)*snap;
11677 		newWidth = Math.min(newWidth,this.options.maxWidth);
11678 		var newHeight = n2i.getInnerHeight()-this.options.perimeter;
11679 		newHeight = Math.floor(newHeight/snap)*snap;
11680 		newHeight = Math.min(newHeight,this.options.maxHeight);
11681 		var maxWidth = 0;
11682 		var maxHeight = 0;
11683 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
11684 			var dims = this.getLargestSize({width:newWidth,height:newHeight},this.images[i]);
11685 			maxWidth = Math.max(maxWidth,dims.width);
11686 			maxHeight = Math.max(maxHeight,dims.height);
11687 		};
11688 		newHeight = Math.round(Math.min(newHeight,maxHeight));
11689 		newWidth = Math.round(Math.min(newWidth,maxWidth));
11690 		
11691 		if (newWidth!=this.width || newHeight!=this.height) {
11692 			this.width = newWidth;
11693 			this.height = newHeight;
11694 			this.dirty = true;
11695 		}
11696 	},
11697 	showById: function(id) {
11698 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
11699 			if (this.images[i].id==id) {
11700 				this.show(i);
11701 				break;
11702 			}
11703 		};
11704 	},
11705 	show: function(index) {
11706 		this.index = index || 0;
11707 		this.calculateSize();
11708 		this.updateUI();
11709 		var space = this.shouldShowController() ? 50 : 10;
11710 		this.element.setStyle({width:(this.width+10)+'px',height:(this.height+space)+'px'});
11711 		this.viewer.setStyle({width:(this.width+10)+'px',height:this.height+'px'});
11712 		this.innerViewer.setStyle({width:((this.width+10)*this.images.length)+'px',height:this.height+'px'});
11713 		this.controller.setStyle({paddingLeft:((this.width-115)/2+5)+'px'});
11714 		this.box.show();
11715 		this.goToImage(false,0,false);
11716 		Event.observe(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
11717 	},
11718 	hide: function(index) {
11719 		this.pause();
11720 		this.box.hide();
11721 		Event.stopObserving(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
11722 	},
11723 	boxCurtainWasClicked : function() {
11724 		this.hide();
11725 	},
11726 	updateUI : function() {
11727 		if (this.dirty) {
11728 			this.innerViewer.innerHTML='';
11729 			for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
11730 				var url = this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[i]);
11731 				url = url.replace(/&/,'&');
11732 				var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_imageviewer_image'}).setStyle({'width':(this.width+10)+'px','height':this.height+'px'});
11733 				
11734 				var url = this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[i]);
11735 				url = url.replace(/&/g,'&');
11736 				this.innerViewer.appendChild(element);
11737 			};
11738 			if (this.shouldShowController()) {
11739 				this.controller.show();
11740 			} else {
11741 				this.controller.hide();
11742 			}
11743 			this.dirty = false;
11744 			this.preload();
11745 		}
11746 	},
11747 	shouldShowController : function() {
11748 		return this.images.length>1;
11749 	},
11750 	goToImage : function(animate,num,user) {	
11751 		if (animate) {
11752 			if (num>1) {
11753 				n2i.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+10),Math.min(num*this.options.transitionReturn,2000),{ease:this.options.easeReturn});				
11754 			} else {
11755 				var end = this.index==0 || this.index==this.images.length-1;
11756 				var ease = (end ? this.options.easeEnd : this.options.ease);
11757 				if (!user) ease = this.options.easeAuto;
11758 				n2i.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+10),(end ? this.options.transitionEnd : this.options.transition),{ease:ease});
11759 			}
11760 		} else {
11761 			this.viewer.scrollLeft=this.index*(this.width+10);
11762 		}
11763 		var text = this.images[this.index].text;
11764 		if (text) {
11765 			this.text.update(text).show();			
11766 		} else {
11767 			this.text.update().hide();
11768 		}
11769 	},
11770 	clearImages : function() {
11771 		this.images = [];
11772 		this.dirty = true;
11773 	},
11774 	addImages : function(images) {
11775 		for (var i=0; i < images.length; i++) {
11776 			this.addImage(images[i]);
11777 		};
11778 	},
11779 	addImage : function(img) {
11780 		this.images.push(img);
11781 		this.dirty = true;
11782 	},
11783 	resolveImageUrl : function(img) {
11784 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
11785 			if (this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl) {
11786 				return this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl(img,this.width,this.height);
11787 			}
11788 		};
11789 		return null;
11790 	},
11791 	play : function() {
11792 		if (!this.interval) {
11793 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
11794 		}
11795 		this.next(false);
11796 		this.playing=true;
11797 		this.playControl.className='in2igui_imageviewer_pause';
11798 	},
11799 	pause : function() {
11800 		window.clearInterval(this.interval);
11801 		this.interval = null;
11802 		this.playControl.className='in2igui_imageviewer_play';
11803 		this.playing = false;
11804 	},
11805 	playOrPause : function() {
11806 		if (this.playing) {
11807 			this.pause();
11808 		} else {
11809 			this.play();
11810 		}
11811 	},
11812 	resetPlay : function() {
11813 		if (this.playing) {
11814 			window.clearInterval(this.interval);
11815 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
11816 		}
11817 	},
11818 	previous : function(user) {
11819 		var num = 1;
11820 		this.index--;
11821 		if (this.index<0) {
11822 			this.index=this.images.length-1;
11823 			num = this.images.length-1;
11824 		}
11825 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
11826 		this.resetPlay();
11827 	},
11828 	next : function(user) {
11829 		var num = 1;
11830 		this.index++;
11831 		if (this.index==this.images.length) {
11832 			this.index=0;
11833 			num = this.images.length-1;
11834 		}
11835 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
11836 		this.resetPlay();
11837 	},
11838 	preload : function() {
11839 		var guiLoader = new n2i.Preloader();
11840 		guiLoader.addImages(In2iGui.context+'In2iGui/gfx/imageviewer_controls.png');
11841 		var self = this;
11842 		guiLoader.setDelegate({allImagesDidLoad:function() {self.preloadImages()}});
11843 		guiLoader.load();
11844 	},
11845 	preloadImages : function() {
11846 		this.loader = new n2i.Preloader();
11847 		this.loader.setDelegate(this);
11848 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
11849 			this.loader.addImages(this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[i]));
11850 		};
11851 		this.status.innerHTML = '0%';
11852 		this.status.style.display='';
11853 		this.loader.load();
11854 	},
11855 	allImagesDidLoad : function() {
11856 		this.status.style.display='none';
11857 	},
11858 	imageDidLoad : function(loaded,total,index) {
11859 		this.status.innerHTML = Math.round(loaded/total*100)+'%';
11860 		var url = this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[index]);
11861 		url = url.replace(/&/g,'&');
11862 		this.innerViewer.childNodes[index].style.backgroundImage="url('"+url+"')";
11863 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_abort',false);
11864 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_error',false);
11865 	},
11866 	imageDidGiveError : function(loaded,total,index) {
11867 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_error',true);
11868 	},
11869 	imageDidAbort : function(loaded,total,index) {
11870 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_abort',true);
11871 	}

11912 		});
11913 	},
11914 	setObjects : function(objects) {
11915 		this.selected = null;
11916 		this.objects = objects || [];
11917 		this.updateUI();
11918 	},
11919 	setValue : function(value) {
11920 		this.value = value;
11921 		this.updateSelection();
11922 	},
11923 	reset : function() {
11924 		this.value = null;
11925 		this.updateSelection();
11926 	},
11927 	updateUI : function() {
11928 		var self = this;
11929 		this.content.update();
11930 		this.container.scrollLeft=0;
11931 		this.container.setStyle({width:this.options.itemsVisible*(this.options.itemWidth+14)+'px'});
11932 		this.container.style.height=(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px';
11933 		this.content.style.width=(this.objects.length*(this.options.itemWidth+14))+'px';
11934 		this.content.style.height=(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px';
11935 		this.objects.each(function(object,i) {
11936 			var item = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_picker_item',title:object.title});
11937 			if (self.value!=null && object[self.options.valueProperty]==self.value) item.addClassName('in2igui_picker_item_selected');
11938 			item.update(
11939 				'<div class="in2igui_picker_item_middle"><div class="in2igui_picker_item_middle">'+
11940 				'<div style="width:'+self.options.itemWidth+'px;height:'+self.options.itemHeight+'px;background-image:url(\''+object.image+'\')"></div>'+
11941 				'</div></div>'+
11942 				'<div class="in2igui_picker_item_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>'
11943 			);
11944 			item.observe('mouseup',function() {self.selectionChanged(object[self.options.valueProperty])});
11945 			self.content.insert(item);			
11946 		});
11947 	},
11948 	updateSelection : function() {
11949 		var children = this.content.childNodes;
11950 		for (var i=0; i < children.length; i++) {
11951 			Element.setClassName(children[i],'in2igui_picker_item_selected',this.value!=null && this.objects[i][this.options.valueProperty]==this.value);
11952 		};
11953 	},
11954 	selectionChanged : function(value) {
11955 		if (this.dragging) return;
11956 		if (this.value==value) return;
11957 		this.value = value;
11958 		this.updateSelection();
11959 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectionChanged',value);
11960 	},
11961 	
11962 	// Dragging
11963 	startDrag : function(e) {
11964 		e.stop();
11965 		var self = this;
11966 		this.dragX = Event.pointerX(e);
11967 		this.dragScroll = this.container.scrollLeft;
11968 		In2iGui.Picker.mousemove = function(e) {self.drag(e);return false;}
11969 		In2iGui.Picker.mouseup = In2iGui.Picker.mousedown = function(e) {self.endDrag(e);return false;}
11970 		window.document.observe('mousemove',In2iGui.Picker.mousemove);
11971 		window.document.observe('mouseup',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
11972 		window.document.observe('mousedown',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
11973 	},
11974 	drag : function(e) {
11975 		this.dragging = true;
11976 		Event.stop(e);
11977 		this.container.scrollLeft=this.dragX-e.pointerX()+this.dragScroll;
11978 	},
11979 	endDrag : function(e) {
11980 		this.dragging = false;
11981 		Event.stop(e);
11982 		window.document.stopObserving('mousemove',In2iGui.Picker.mousemove);
11983 		window.document.stopObserving('mouseup',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
11984 		window.document.stopObserving('mousedown',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
11985 		var size = (this.options.itemWidth+14);
11986 		n2i.ani(this.container,'scrollLeft',Math.round(this.container.scrollLeft/size)*size,500,{ease:n2i.ease.bounceOut});
11987 	}
11988 }

12009 In2iGui.Editor.prototype = {
12010 	ignite : function() {
12011 		this.reload();
12012 	},
12013 	addPartController : function(key,title,controller) {
12014 		this.partControllers.push({key:key,'title':title,'controller':controller});
12015 	},
12016 	getPartController : function(key) {
12017 		var ctrl = null;
12018 		this.partControllers.each(function(item) {
12019 			if (item.key==key) ctrl=item;
12020 		});
12021 		return ctrl;
12022 	},
12023 	reload : function() {
12024 		if (this.partControls) {
12025 			this.partControls.hide();
12026 		}
12027 		var self = this;
12028 		this.parts = [];
12029 		var rows = $$('.row');
12030 		rows.each(function(row,i) {
12031 			var columns = row.select('.column');
12032 			self.reloadColumns(columns,i);
12033 			columns.each(function(column,j) {
12034 				var parts = column.select('.part');
12035 				self.reloadParts(parts,i,j);
12036 			});
12037 		});
12038 		var parts = $$('.part');
12039 		
12040 		this.parts.each(function(part) {
12041 			var i = parts.indexOf(part.element);
12042 			if (i!=-1) delete(parts[i]);
12043 		});
12044 		this.reloadParts(parts,-1,-1);
12045 	},
12046 	partExists : function(element) {
12047 		
12048 	},
12049 	reloadColumns : function(columns,rowIndex) {
12050 		var self = this;
12051 		columns.each(function(column,columnIndex) {
12052 			column.observe('mouseover',function() {
12053 				self.hoverColumn(column);
12054 			});
12055 			column.observe('mouseout',function() {
12056 				self.blurColumn();
12057 			});
12058 			column.observe('contextmenu',function(e) {
12059 				self.contextColumn(column,rowIndex,columnIndex,e);
12060 			});
12061 		});
12062 	},
12063 	reloadParts : function(parts,row,column) {
12064 		var self = this;
12065 		parts.each(function(element,partIndex) {
12066 			if (!element) return;
12067 			var match = element.className.match(/part_([\w]+)/i);
12068 			if (match && match[1]) {
12069 				var handler = self.getPartController(match[1]);
12070 				if (handler) {
12071 					var part = new handler.controller(element,row,column,partIndex);
12072 					part.type=match[1];
12073 					element.observe('click',function() {
12074 						self.editPart(part);
12075 					});
12076 					element.observe('mouseover',function(e) {
12077 						self.hoverPart(part);
12078 					});
12079 					element.observe('mouseout',function(e) {
12080 						self.blurPart(e);
12081 					});
12082 					element.observe('mousedown',function(e) {
12083 						self.startPartDrag(e);
12084 					});
12085 					self.parts.push(part);
12086 				}
12087 			}
12088 		});
12089 	},
12090 	activate : function() {
12091 		this.active = true;
12092 	},
12093 	deactivate : function() {
12094 		this.active = false;
12095 		if (this.activePart) {
12096 			this.activePart.deactivate();
12097 		}
12098 		if (this.partControls) this.partControls.hide();
12099 	},

12398 In2iGui.Editor.startDrag = function(e,element) {
12399 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement = element;
12400 	Element.observe(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.Editor.dragListener);
12401 	Element.observe(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener);
12402 	In2iGui.Editor.startDragPos = {top:e.pointerY(),left:e.pointerX()};
12403 	e.stop();
12404 	return false;
12405 }
12406 
12407 In2iGui.Editor.dragListener = function(e) {
12408 	var element = In2iGui.Editor.dragElement;
12409 	element.style.left = e.pointerX()+'px';
12410 	element.style.top = e.pointerY()+'px';
12411 	element.style.display='block';
12412 	return false;
12413 }
12414 
12415 In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener = function(event) {
12416 	Event.stopObserving(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.Editor.dragListener);
12417 	Event.stopObserving(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener);
12418 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement.style.display='none';
12419 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement=null;
12420 }

12422 In2iGui.Editor.getPartId = function(element) {
12423 	var m = element.id.match(/part\-([\d]+)/i);
12424 	if (m && m.length>0) return m[1];
12425 }

12439 In2iGui.Editor.Header.prototype = {

12441 		this.value = this.header.innerHTML;
12442 		this.field = new Element('textarea').addClassName('in2igui_editor_header');
12443 		this.field.value = this.value;
12444 		this.header.style.visibility='hidden';
12445 		this.updateFieldStyle();
12446 		this.element.insertBefore(this.field,this.header);
12447 		this.field.focus();
12448 		this.field.select();
12449 		this.field.observe('keydown',function(e) {
12450 			if (e.keyCode==Event.KEY_RETURN) {
12451 				this.save();
12452 			}
12453 		}.bind(this));
12454 	},
12455 	save : function() {
12456 		var value = this.field.value;
12457 		this.header.innerHTML = value;
12458 		this.deactivate();
12459 		if (value!=this.value) {
12460 			this.value = value;
12461 			In2iGui.Editor.get().partChanged(this);
12462 		}
12463 	},
12464 	cancel : function() {
12465 		this.deactivate();
12466 	},
12467 	deactivate : function() {
12468 		this.header.style.visibility='';
12469 		this.element.removeChild(this.field);
12470 		In2iGui.Editor.get().partDidDeacivate(this);
12471 	},
12472 	updateFieldStyle : function() {
12473 		this.field.setStyle({width:this.header.getWidth()+'px',height:this.header.getHeight()+'px'});
12474 		n2i.copyStyle(this.header,this.field,['fontSize','marginTop','fontWeight','fontFamily','textAlign','color','fontStyle']);
12475 	},
12476 	getValue : function() {
12477 		return this.value;
12478 	}
12479 }

12492 In2iGui.Editor.Html.prototype = {

12497 		this.element.update('');

12501 		this.element.appendChild(this.editor.getElement());
12502 		this.editor.addDelegate(this);
12503 		this.editor.ignite();

12511 			,'fontSize':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-size')
12512 			,'fontWeight':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-weight')
12513 			,'color':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'color')
12514 		}
12515 	},
12516 	cancel : function() {
12517 		this.deactivate();
12518 		this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
12519 	},
12520 	save : function() {

12522 		var value = this.editor.value;
12523 		if (value!=this.value) {
12524 			this.value = value;
12525 			In2iGui.Editor.get().partChanged(this);
12526 		}
12527 		this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
12528 	},
12529 	deactivate : function() {
12530 		if (this.editor) {
12531 			this.editor.deactivate();
12532 			this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
12533 		}
12534 		In2iGui.Editor.get().partDidDeacivate(this);
12535 	},
12536 	richTextDidChange : function() {
12537 		//this.deactivate();
12538 	},
12539 	getValue : function() {
12540 		return this.value;
12541 	}

12556 In2iGui.Menu.create = function(name,options) {
12557 	options = options || {};

12563 
12564 In2iGui.Menu.prototype = {
12565 	addBehavior : function() {
12566 		var self = this;
12567 		this.hider = function() {
12568 			self.hide();
12569 		}
12570 		if (this.options.autoHide) {
12571 			var x = function(e) {
12572 				if (!In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.element) && (!self.options.parentElement || !In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.options.parentElement))) {
12573 					if (!self.isSubMenuVisible()) {
12574 						self.hide();
12575 					}
12576 				}
12577 			};
12578 			this.element.observe('mouseout',x);
12579 			if (this.options.parentElement) {
12580 				this.options.parentElement.observe('mouseout',x);
12581 			}
12582 		}
12583 	},
12584 	addDivider : function() {
12585 		this.element.insert(new Element('div').addClassName('in2igui_menu_divider'));
12586 	},
12587 	addItem : function(item) {
12588 		var self = this;
12589 		var element = new Element('div').addClassName('in2igui_menu_item').update(item.title);
12590 		element.observe('click',function(e) {
12591 			self.itemWasClicked(item.value);
12592 			Event.stop(e);
12593 		});
12594 		if (item.children) {
12595 			var sub = In2iGui.Menu.create(null,{autoHide:true,parentElement:element});
12596 			sub.addItems(item.children);
12597 			element.observe('mouseover',function(e) {
12598 				sub.showAtElement(element,e,'horizontal');
12599 			});
12600 			//sub.addDelegate({itemWasClicked:function(value) {self.itemWasClicked(value)}});
12601 			self.subMenus.push(sub);
12602 			element.addClassName('in2igui_menu_item_children');
12603 		}
12604 		this.element.insert(element);
12605 	},
12606 	addItems : function(items) {
12607 		for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
12608 			if (items[i]==null) {
12609 				this.addDivider();
12610 			} else {
12611 				this.addItem(items[i]);
12612 			}
12613 		};
12614 	},
12615 	getValue : function() {
12616 		return this.value;
12617 	},
12618 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
12619 		this.value = value;
12620 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'itemWasClicked',value);
12621 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'select',value);
12622 		this.hide();
12623 	},
12624 	showAtPointer : function(event) {
12625 		if (event) {
12626 			Event.stop(event);
12627 			//if (event.type!='click') this.ignoreNextClick=true;
12628 		}
12629 		this.showAtPoint({'top':event.pointerY(),'left':event.pointerX()});
12630 	},
12631 	showAtElement : function(element,event,position) {
12632 		if (event) {
12633 			Event.stop(event);
12634 		}
12635 		var point = element.cumulativeOffset();
12636 		if (position=='horizontal') {
12637 			point.left += element.getWidth();
12638 		} else if (position=='vertical') {
12639 			point.top += element.getHeight();
12640 		}
12641 		this.showAtPoint(point);
12642 	},
12643 	showAtPoint : function(pos) {
12644 		var innerWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth();
12645 		var innerHeight = n2i.getInnerHeight();
12646 		var scrollTop = n2i.getScrollTop();
12647 		var scrollLeft = n2i.getScrollLeft();
12648 		if (!this.visible) {
12649 			this.element.setStyle({'display':'block','visibility':'hidden',opacity:0});
12650 		}
12651 		var width = this.element.getWidth();
12652 		var height = this.element.getHeight();
12653 		this.element.setStyle({'top':Math.min(pos.top,innerHeight-height-20+scrollTop)+'px','left':Math.min(pos.left,innerWidth-width-20+scrollLeft)+'px','visibility':'visible',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex()});
12654 		if (!this.visible) {
12655 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,200);
12656 			this.addHider();
12657 			this.visible = true;
12658 		}
12659 	},
12660 	hide : function() {
12661 		if (!this.visible) return;
12662 		var self = this;
12663 		n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',0,200,{onComplete:function() {
12664 			self.element.setStyle({'display':'none'});
12665 		}})
12666 		this.removeHider();
12667 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
12668 			this.subMenus[i].hide();
12669 		};
12670 		this.visible = false;
12671 	},
12672 	isSubMenuVisible : function() {
12673 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
12674 			if (this.subMenus[i].visible) return true;
12675 		};
12676 		return false;
12677 	},
12678 	addHider : function() {
12679 		Element.observe(document.body,'click',this.hider);
12680 	},
12681 	removeHider : function() {
12682 		Event.stopObserving(document.body,'click',this.hider);
12683 	}
12684 }

12705 In2iGui.Overlay.prototype = {
12706 	addBehavior : function() {
12707 		var self = this;
12708 		this.hider = function(e) {
12709 			if (self.boundElement) {
12710 				if (In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.boundElement) || In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.element)) return;
12711 				// TODO: should be unreg'ed but it fails
12712 				//self.boundElement.stopObserving(self.hider);
12713 				self.boundElement.removeClassName('in2igui_overlay_bound');
12714 				self.boundElement = null;
12715 				self.hide();
12716 			}
12717 		}
12718 		this.element.observe('mouseout',this.hider);
12719 	},
12720 	addIcon : function(key,icon) {
12721 		var self = this;
12722 		var element = new Element('div').addClassName('in2igui_overlay_icon');
12723 		element.setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(icon,2)+')'});
12724 		element.observe('click',function(e) {
12725 			self.iconWasClicked(key,e);
12726 		});
12727 		this.icons.set(key,element);
12728 		this.content.insert(element);
12729 	},
12730 	hideIcons : function(keys) {
12731 		var self = this;
12732 		keys.each(function(key) {
12733 			self.icons.get(key).hide();
12734 		});
12735 	},
12736 	showIcons : function(keys) {
12737 		var self = this;
12738 		keys.each(function(key) {
12739 			self.icons.get(key).show();
12740 		});
12741 	},
12742 	iconWasClicked : function(key,e) {
12743 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'iconWasClicked',key,e);
12744 	},
12745 	showAtElement : function(element,options) {
12746 		In2iGui.positionAtElement(this.element,element,options);
12747 		if (this.visible) return;
12748 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {
12749 			this.element.setStyle({'display':'block'});
12750 		} else {
12751 			this.element.setStyle({'display':'block','opacity':0});
12752 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,150);
12753 		}
12754 		this.visible = true;
12755 		if (options.autoHide) {
12756 			this.boundElement = element;
12757 			element.observe('mouseout',this.hider);
12758 			element.addClassName('in2igui_overlay_bound');
12759 		}
12760 		return;
12761 	},
12762 	hide : function() {
12763 		this.element.setStyle({'display':'none'});
12764 		this.visible = false;
12765 	}
12766 }

12769 /**
12770  * @class
12771  *
12772  * Options
12773  * {url:'',parameters:{}}

12775  * Events:
12776  * uploadDidCompleteQueue
12777  * uploadDidStartQueue
12778  * uploadDidComplete(file)
12779  */
12780 In2iGui.Upload = function(o) {
12781 	o = this.options = n2i.override({url:'',parameters:{}},o);
12782 	this.element = $(o.element);
12783 	this.itemContainer = this.element.select('.in2igui_upload_items')[0];
12784 	this.status = this.element.select('.in2igui_upload_status')[0];
12785 	this.name = o.name;
12786 	this.items = [];
12787 	this.busy = false;
12788 	this.loaded = false;
12789 	this.flashMode = swfobject.hasFlashPlayerVersion("8");
12790 	In2iGui.extend(this);
12791 	this.addBehavior();
12792 }

12794 In2iGui.Upload.create = function(o) {

12799 		'<div class="in2igui_upload_status"></div>'+
12800 	'</div>');

12803 
12804 In2iGui.Upload.prototype = {
12805 	addBehavior : function() {
12806 		var self = this;
12807 		if (!this.flashMode) {
12808 			this.createIframeVersion();
12809 			return;
12810 		}
12811 		if (In2iGui.get().domLoaded) {
12812 			this.createFlashVersion();			
12813 		} else {
12814 			In2iGui.onDomReady(function() {self.createFlashVersion()});
12815 		}
12816 	},
12817 	
12818 	/////////////////////////// Iframe //////////////////////////
12819 	
12820 	createIframeVersion : function() {
12821 		var container = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_upload'});
12822 		var form = new Element('form',{'action':this.options.url || '', 'method':'post', 'enctype':'multipart/form-data','encoding':'multipart/form-data','target':'upload'});
12823 		if (this.options.parameters) {
12824 			$H(this.options.parameters).each(function(pair) {
12825 				var hidden = new Element('input',{'type':'hidden','name':pair.key});
12826 				hidden.setValue(pair.value);
12827 				form.insert(hidden);
12828 			});
12829 		}
12830 		var file = new Element('input',{'type':'file','class':'file','name':this.options.name});
12831 		var self = this;
12832 		file.onchange = function() {self.iframeSubmit()}
12833 		form.insert(file);
12834 		container.insert(form);
12835 		var iframe = new Element('iframe',{name:'upload',id:'upload'}).setStyle({display:'none'});
12836 		iframe.observe('load',function() {self.iframeUploadComplete()});
12837 		container.insert(iframe);
12838 		this.progressBar = In2iGui.ProgressBar.create();
12839 		this.progressBar.hide();
12840 		container.insert(this.progressBar.getElement());
12841 		this.form = form;
12842 		this.element.insert(container);
12843 	},
12844 	iframeUploadComplete : function() {
12845 		if (!this.uploading) return;
12846 		this.uploading = false;
12847 		this.form.reset();
12848 		this.fire('uploadDidCompleteQueue');
12849 	},
12850 	iframeSubmit : function() {
12851 		this.uploading = true;
12852 		// IE: set value of parms again since they disappear
12853 		var p = this.options.parameters;
12854 		for (var i=0; i < p.length; i++) {
12855 			this.form[p[i].name].value=p[i].value;
12856 		};
12857 		this.form.submit();
12858 		this.fire('uploadDidSubmit');
12859 	},
12860 	startProgress : function() {
12861 		this.form.style.display='none';
12862 		this.progressBar.show();
12863 	},
12864 	setProgress : function(value) {
12865 		this.progressBar.setValue(value);
12866 	},
12867 	endProgress : function() {
12868 		this.form.style.display='block';
12869 		this.form.reset();
12870 		this.progressBar.reset();
12871 		this.progressBar.hide();
12872 	},
12873 	
12874 	parentShown : function() {
12875 		this.updateButtonPosition();
12876 	},
12877 	clear : function() {
12878 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
12879 			if (this.items[i]) {
12880 				this.items[i].destroy();
12881 			}
12882 		};
12883 		this.items = [];
12884 		this.itemContainer.hide();
12885 		this.status.update();
12886 	},
12887 	
12888 	/////////////////////////// Flash //////////////////////////
12889 	
12890 	createFlashVersion : function() {
12891 		var loc = new String(document.location);
12892 		var url = loc.slice(0,loc.lastIndexOf('/')+1);
12893 		url += this.options.url;
12894 		var session = n2i.cookie.get('JSESSIONID');
12895 		if (session) {
12896 			url+=';jsessionid='+session;
12897 		}
12898 		//var size = this.button.getDimensions();
12899 		var size = {width:108,height:28};
12900 		var self = this;
12901 		this.loader = new SWFUpload({
12902 			upload_url : url,
12903 			flash_url : In2iGui.context+"/In2iGui/lib/swfupload/swfupload.swf",
12904 			file_size_limit : "20480",
12905 			file_upload_limit : 100,
12906 			debug : true,
12907 			post_params : this.options.parameters,
12908 			button_placeholder_id : 'x',
12909 			button_placeholder : this.element.select('.in2igui_upload_placeholder')[0],
12910 			button_width : size.width,
12911 			button_height : size.height,
12912 
12913 			swfupload_loaded_handler : function() {self.flashLoaded()},
12914 			file_queued_handler : self.fileQueued.bind(self),
12915 			file_queue_error_handler : function(file, error, message) {self.fileQueueError(file, error, message)},
12916 			file_dialog_complete_handler : function() {self.fileDialogComplete()},
12917 			upload_start_handler : function() {self.uploadStart()},
12918 			upload_progress_handler : function(file,complete,total) {self.uploadProgress(file,complete,total)},
12919 			upload_error_handler : function(file, error, message) {self.uploadError(file, error, message)},
12920 			upload_success_handler : function(file,data) {self.uploadSuccess(file,data)},
12921 			upload_complete_handler : function(file) {self.uploadComplete(file)},
12922 		
12923 			// SWFObject settings
12924 			swfupload_pre_load_handler : function() {alert('swfupload_pre_load_handler!')},
12925 			swfupload_load_failed_handler : function() {alert('swfupload_load_failed_handler!')}
12926 		});
12927 		if (this.options.button) {
12928 			this.setButton(In2iGui.get(this.options.button));
12929 		}
12930 	},
12931 	setButton : function(widget) {
12932 		this.button = widget;
12933 		if (this.button && this.flashMode) {
12934 			var m = this.element.select('object')[0].remove();
12935 			m.setStyle({width:'108px','marginLeft':'-108px',position:'absolute'});
12936 			widget.getElement().insert(m);
12937 			return;
12938 		}
12939 	},
12940 	updateButtonPosition : function() {
12941 		if (this.button) {
12942 			var f = this.button.element.select('object')[0];
12943 			if (f) {
12944 				var w = this.button.element.getWidth();
12945 				f.setStyle({width:w+'px','marginLeft':'-'+w+'px',position:'absolute'})
12946 			}
12947 		}
12948 	},
12949 	startNextUpload : function() {
12950 		this.loader.startUpload();
12951 	},
12952 	addError : function(error,file) {
12953 		var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_upload_item_error'});
12954 		element.insert(new Element('a',{'class':'in2igui_link'}).update('<span>Fjern</span>').observe('click',function() {this.parentNode.remove(); return false;}));
12955 		element.insert('<strong>'+In2iGui.Upload.errors[error]+'</strong><br/><em>'+file.name+'</em>');
12956 		this.itemContainer.insert(element);
12957 	},
12958 	
12959 	//////////////////// Events //////////////
12960 	
12961 	flashLoaded : function() {
12962 		this.loaded = true;
12963 	},
12964 	fileQueued : function(file) {
12965 		var item = new In2iGui.Upload.Item(file);
12966 		this.items[file.index] = item;
12967 		this.itemContainer.insert(item.element);
12968 		this.itemContainer.setStyle({display:'block'});
12969 	},
12970 	fileQueueError : function(file, error, message) {
12971 		this.addError(error,file);
12972 	},
12973 	fileDialogComplete : function() {
12974 		this.startNextUpload();
12975 	},
12976 	uploadStart : function() {
12977 		if (!this.busy) {
12978 			this.fire('uploadDidStartQueue');
12979 		}
12980 		this.busy = true;
12981 	},
12982 	uploadProgress : function(file,complete,total) {
12983 		this.updateStatus();
12984 		this.items[file.index].updateProgress(complete,total);
12985 	},
12986 	uploadError : function(file, error, message) {
12987 		if (file) {
12988 			this.items[file.index].update(file);
12989 		}
12990 	},
12991 	uploadSuccess : function(file,data) {
12992 		this.items[file.index].updateProgress(file.size,file.size);
12993 	},
12994 	uploadComplete : function(file) {
12995 		this.items[file.index].update(file);
12996 		this.startNextUpload();
12997 		var self = this;
12998 		this.fire('uploadDidComplete',file);
12999 		if (this.loader.getStats().files_queued==0) {

13126 /* EOF */In2iGui.Gallery = function(id,name,options) {
13127 	this.id = id;
13128 	this.name = name;
13129 	this.options = options || {};
13130 	this.element = $(id);
13131 	this.objects = [];
13132 	this.nodes = [];
13133 	this.selected = new Hash();
13134 	this.width = 100;
13135 	this.height = 100;
13136 	In2iGui.extend(this);
13137 }
13138 
13139 In2iGui.Gallery.prototype = {
13140 	setObjects : function(objects) {
13141 		this.objects = objects;
13142 		this.render();
13143 	},
13144 	getObjects : function() {
13145 		return this.objects;
13146 	},
13147 	render : function() {
13148 		this.nodes = [];
13149 		this.element.update();
13150 		var self = this;
13151 		this.objects.each(function(object,i) {
13152 			var url = self.resolveImageUrl(object);
13153 			url = url.replace(/&/,'&');
13154 			if (object.height<object.width) {
13155 				var top = (self.height-(self.height*object.height/object.width))/2;
13156 			} else {
13157 				var top = 0;
13158 			}
13159 			var img = new Element('img',{src:url}).setStyle({margin:top+'px auto 0px'});
13160 			var item = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_gallery_item'}).setStyle({'width':self.width+'px','height':self.height+'px'}).insert(img);
13161 			item.observe('click',function() {
13162 				self.itemClicked(i);
13163 			});
13164 			item.observe('dblclick',function() {
13165 				self.itemDoubleClicked(i);
13166 			});
13167 			self.element.insert(item);
13168 			self.nodes.push(item);
13169 		});
13170 	},
13171 	updateUI : function() {
13172 		var self = this;
13173 		this.objects.each(function(object,i) {
13174 			if (self.selected.get(i)) {
13175 				self.nodes[i].addClassName('in2igui_gallery_item_selected');
13176 			} else {
13177 				self.nodes[i].removeClassName('in2igui_gallery_item_selected');
13178 			}
13179 		});
13180 	},
13181 	resolveImageUrl : function(img) {
13182 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
13183 			if (this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl) {
13184 				return this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl(img,this.width,this.height);
13185 			}
13186 		};
13187 		return '';
13188 	},
13189 	itemClicked : function(index) {
13190 		this.selected = new Hash();
13191 		this.selected.set(index,true);
13192 		this.updateUI();
13193 	},
13194 	itemDoubleClicked : function(index) {
13195 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'itemOpened',this.objects[index]);
13196 	}
13197 }

13212 In2iGui.Calendar.prototype = {
13213 	getFirstDay : function() {
13214 		var date = new Date(this.date.getTime());
13215 		date.setDate(date.getDate()-date.getDay()+1);
13216 		date.setHours(0);
13217 		date.setMinutes(0);
13218 		date.setSeconds(0);
13219 		return date;
13220 	},
13221 	getLastDay : function() {
13222 		var date = new Date(this.date.getTime());
13223 		date.setDate(date.getDate()-date.getDay()+7);
13224 		date.setHours(23);
13225 		date.setMinutes(59);
13226 		date.setSeconds(59);
13227 		return date;
13228 	},
13229 	clearEvents : function() {
13230 		this.events = [];
13231 		var nodes = this.element.select('.in2igui_calendar_event');
13232 		nodes.each(function(node) {
13233 			node.remove();
13234 		});
13235 		this.hideEventViewer();
13236 	},
13237 	setEvents : function(events) {
13238 		this.setBusy(false);
13239 		this.clearEvents();
13240 		this.events = events;
13241 		var self = this;
13242 		var pixels = (this.options.endHour-this.options.startHour)*40;
13243 		this.events.each(function(event) {
13244 			var day = self.body.select('.day')[event.startTime.getDay()-1];
13245 			var node = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event'});
13246 			var top = ((event.startTime.getHours()*60+event.startTime.getMinutes())/60-self.options.startHour)*40-1;
13247 			var height = (event.endTime.getTime()-event.startTime.getTime())/1000/60/60*40+1;
13248 			var height = Math.min(pixels-top,height);
13249 			node.setStyle({'marginTop':top+'px','height':height+'px'});
13250 			var content = new Element('div');
13251 			content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_time'}).update(event.startTime.dateFormat('H:i')));
13252 			content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_text'}).update(event.text));
13253 			if (event.location) {
13254 				content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_location'}).update(event.location));
13255 			}
13256 			day.insert(node.insert(content));
13257 			node.observe('click',function() {
13258 				self.eventWasClicked(event,this);
13259 			});
13260 		});
13261 	},
13262 	eventWasClicked : function(event,node) {
13263 		this.showEvent(event,node);
13264 	},
13265 	setBusy : function(busy) {

13267 			this.element.addClassName('in2igui_calendar_busy');
13268 		} else {
13269 			this.element.removeClassName('in2igui_calendar_busy');
13270 		}
13271 	},
13272 	updateUI : function() {
13273 		var first = this.getFirstDay();
13274 		var x = this.head.select('.time')[0];
13275 		x.update('<div>Uge '+this.date.getWeekOfYear()+' '+this.date.getFullYear()+'</div>');
13276 		
13277 		var days = this.head.select('.day');
13278 		for (var i=0; i < days.length; i++) {
13279 			var date = new Date(first.getTime());
13280 			date.setDate(date.getDate()+i);
13281 			days[i].update(date.dateFormat('l \\d. d M'))
13282 		};
13283 	},
13284 	buildUI : function() {
13285 		var bar = this.element.select('.in2igui_calendar_bar')[0];

13292 		today.addDelegate(this);
13293 		this.toolbar.add(today);
13294 		var next = In2iGui.Button.create('in2iguiCalendarNext',{text:'',icon:'monochrome/next'});

13302 		for (var i=this.options.startHour; i <= this.options.endHour; i++) {
13303 			var node = new Element('div').update('<span><em>'+i+':00</em></span>');
13304 			if (i==this.options.startHour) {
13305 				node.addClassName('first');

13307 			if (i==this.options.endHour) {
13308 				node.addClassName('last');

13402 In2iGui.DatePicker = function(id,name,options) {

13418 In2iGui.DatePicker.create = function(name,options) {
13419 	var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_datepicker'});
13420 	element.insert('<div class="in2igui_datepicker_header"><a class="in2igui_datepicker_next"></a><a class="in2igui_datepicker_previous"></a><strong></strong></div>');
13421 	var table = new Element('table');
13422 	var head = new Element('tr');
13423 	table.insert(new Element('thead').insert(head));
13424 	for (var i=0;i<7;i++) {
13425 		head.insert(new Element('th').update(Date.dayNames[i].substring(0,3)));
13426 	}
13427 	var body = new Element('tbody');
13428 	table.insert(body);
13429 	for (var i=0;i<6;i++) {
13430 		var row = new Element('tr');
13431 		for (var j=0;j<7;j++) {
13432 			var cell = new Element('td');
13433 			row.insert(cell);
13434 		}
13435 		body.insert(row);
13436 	}
13437 	element.insert(table);
13438 	return new In2iGui.DatePicker(element,name,options);
13439 }

13441 In2iGui.DatePicker.prototype = {
13442 	addBehavior : function() {
13443 		var self = this;
13444 		this.cells = this.element.select('td');
13445 		this.cells.each(function(cell,index) {
13446 			cell.observe('mousedown',function() {self.selectCell(index)});
13447 		})
13448 		this.element.select('.in2igui_datepicker_next')[0].observe('mousedown',function() {self.next()});
13449 		this.element.select('.in2igui_datepicker_previous')[0].observe('mousedown',function() {self.previous()});
13450 	},
13451 	setValue : function(date) {
13452 		this.value = new Date(date.getTime());
13453 		this.viewDate = new Date(date.getTime());
13454 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
13455 		this.updateUI();
13456 	},
13457 	updateUI : function() {
13458 		this.title.update(this.viewDate.dateFormat('F Y'));
13459 		var isSelectedYear =  this.value.getFullYear()==this.viewDate.getFullYear();
13460 		var month = this.viewDate.getMonth();
13461 		for (var i=0; i < this.cells.length; i++) {
13462 			var date = this.indexToDate(i);
13463 			var cell = this.cells[i];
13464 			if (date.getMonth()<month) {
13465 				cell.className = 'in2igui_datepicker_dimmed';
13466 			} else if (date.getMonth()>month) {
13467 				cell.className = 'in2igui_datepicker_dimmed';
13468 			} else {
13469 				cell.className = '';
13470 			}
13471 			if (date.getDate()==this.value.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.value.getMonth() && isSelectedYear) {
13472 				cell.addClassName('in2igui_datepicker_selected');
13473 			}
13474 			if (date.getDate()==this.today.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.today.getMonth() && date.getFullYear()==this.today.getFullYear()) {
13475 				cell.addClassName('in2igui_datepicker_today');
13476 			}
13477 			cell.update(date.getDate());
13478 		};
13479 	},
13480 	getPreviousMonth : function() {
13481 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
13482 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()-1);
13483 		return previous;
13484 	},
13485 	getNextMonth : function() {
13486 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
13487 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()+1);
13488 		return previous;
13489 	},
13490 	////////////////// Events ///////////////
13491 	previous : function() {
13492 		this.viewDate = this.getPreviousMonth();
13493 		this.updateUI();
13494 	},
13495 	next : function() {
13496 		this.viewDate = this.getNextMonth();
13497 		this.updateUI();
13498 	},
13499 	selectCell : function(index) {
13500 		this.value = this.indexToDate(index);
13501 		this.viewDate = new Date(this.value.getTime());
13502 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
13503 		this.updateUI();
13504 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'dateChanged',this.value);
13505 	},
13506 	indexToDate : function(index) {
13507 		var first = this.viewDate.getDay();
13508 		var days = this.viewDate.getDaysInMonth();
13509 		var previousDays = this.getPreviousMonth().getDaysInMonth();
13510 		if (index<first) {
13511 			var date = this.getPreviousMonth();
13512 			date.setDate(previousDays-first+index+1);
13513 			return date;
13514 		} else if (index>first+days-1) {
13515 			var date = this.getPreviousMonth();
13516 			date.setDate(index-first-days+1);
13517 			return date;
13518 			cell.update(i-first-days+1);
13519 		} else {
13520 			var date = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
13521 			date.setDate(index+1-first);
13522 			return date;
13523 		}
13524 	}
13525 }

13562 In2iGui.Columns.prototype = {
13563 	addToColumn : function(index,widget) {
13564 		var c = this.ensureColumn(index);
13565 		c.insert(widget.getElement());
13566 	},
13567 	setColumnStyle : function(index,style) {
13568 		var c = this.ensureColumn(index);
13569 		c.setStyle(style);
13570 	},
13571 	setColumnWidth : function(index,width) {
13572 		var c = this.ensureColumn(index);
13573 		c.setStyle({width:width+'px'});
13574 	},
13575 	ensureColumn : function(index) {
13576 		var children = this.body.childElements();
13577 		for (var i=children.length-1;i<index;i++) {
13578 			this.body.insert(new Element('td',{'class':'in2igui_columns_column'}));
13579 		}
13580 		return this.body.childElements()[index];
13581 	}
13582 }

13611 In2iGui.Box.create = function(name,options) {
13612 	options = n2i.override({},options);
13613 	var e = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_box'});
13614 	if (options.width) e.setStyle({width:options.width+'px'});
13615 	if (options.absolute) e.addClassName('in2igui_box_absolute');
13616 	e.update('<div class="in2igui_box_top"><div><div></div></div></div>'+
13617 		'<div class="in2igui_box_middle"><div class="in2igui_box_middle">'+
13618 		(options.title ? '<div class="in2igui_box_header"><strong class="in2igui_box_title">'+options.title+'</strong></div>' : '')+
13619 		'<div class="in2igui_box_body"'+(options.padding ? ' style="padding: '+options.padding+'px;"' : '')+'></div>'+
13620 		'</div></div>'+
13621 		'<div class="in2igui_box_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>');
13622 	return new In2iGui.Box(e,name,options);
13623 }
13624 
13625 In2iGui.Box.prototype = {
13626 	addToDocument : function() {
13627 		document.body.appendChild(this.element);
13628 	},
13629 	add : function(widget) {
13630 		if (widget.getElement) {
13631 			this.body.insert(widget.getElement());
13632 		} else {
13633 			this.body.insert(widget);
13634 		}
13635 	},
13636 	show : function() {
13637 		var e = this.element;
13638 		if (this.options.modal) {
13639 			var index = In2iGui.nextPanelIndex();
13640 			e.style.zIndex=index+1;
13641 			In2iGui.showCurtain(this,index);
13642 		}
13643 		e.setStyle({display:'block',visibility:'hidden'});
13644 		var w = e.getWidth();
13645 		var top = (n2i.getInnerHeight()-e.getHeight())/2+n2i.getScrollTop();
13646 		e.setStyle({'marginLeft':(w/-2)+'px',top:top+'px'});
13647 		e.setStyle({display:'block',visibility:'visible'});
13648 	},
13649 	hide : function() {
13650 		In2iGui.hideCurtain(this);
13651 		this.element.setStyle({display:'none'});
13652 	},
13653 	curtainWasClicked : function() {
13654 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'boxCurtainWasClicked');
13655 	}
13656 }
